\id REV KUY 66 Soli Bible version 
\h Kuyubulula 
\toc1 Libuku lya Kuyubulula 
\toc2 Kuyubulula 
\toc3 Kuyubulula 
\mt2 Libuku lya 
\mt1 Kuyubulula 
\imt1 Busansulushi 
\ip Libuku lya Kuyubulula elibuku lyakupwililisha mu Cipangano ca Linolino. Lyalapwishiwa kulembwa mu caka ca makumi asanu ne ana ne byaka bisanu panyuma pakusemwa kwa Yesu (A D 95) Ne Yohane Mutumwa Kuy 1:1 kayi eumo umo walalemba Mulumbe Waina wa Yohane ne makalata atatu a 1 Yohane, 2 Yohane ne 3 Yohane.Yohane walikuba weshibikweti “Ngwalikuyandishisha Yesu” Yoh 13:23 Walalemba libuku ili pacindi ncalikuba pa nsumbu ya Patmo nkwalikuba wasungilwa cebo ca kukambauka Mulumbe Waina ulambanga sha Yesu Klistu. Kuy 1:9. 
\ip Cintu cinene ncalalemba mulibuku lya Kuyubulula ni cakubayuminisha balabelengenga kwambeti bapitilishe kushoma muli Yesu Klistu, ne kubapa kupembelela pakwinga kubwela kwa Yesu kuli pepi 1:3, 22:7 Walalembela baklistu bonse, kayi ne ku mibungano isanu ne ibili yabashoma njalashumbula maina mu cimpansha ca 2-3. Yohane lakwambanga kulemba kwakendi mwine kuba maswi abushinshimi Kuy 1:3 kayi lasebenseshenga mikoshano ingi ne bimbonimboni mbyalabona. Libuku ili lyakoshanako kumbasu nashimbi sha mu Cipangano ca Kaindi, makamaka Sekaliya 6:1-8. Tolompita shisanu ne shibili, ne Indilo shisanu ne shibili shakoshana ne malwashi Lesa ngwalabasubula nawo Bainjipito, Kul 7-9 Kuyubulula kulambangaponga sha mapwililisho a cindi nceti akese Yesu kwisakukoma, ne kwisa kumanta bonse bashoma mulyendiye kwambeti bakekale nendi kwamuyayaya, Kamulekani libuku ili limucenjeshe nekumupa kupembelela kwa kwambeti Yesu lesanga linolino. 
\iot Mitwi yamakani 
\io1 Yohane latatikinga kulyamba mwine kwambeti niyani, kayi ne mwalatambwila cimboni mboni cabushinshimi 1:1-20 
\io1 Lapanga mulumbe kufuma kuli Yesu ulenga ku Mibungano isanu ne ibili 1:1 mpaka 3:22 
\io1 Kayi lambanga sha indilo bisanu ne bibili, ne Tolompita asanu ne abili 8:6 mpaka 11:19 
\io1 Panyuma palibi, Yohane lambanga sha nkondo ya Mwana mutuloba kulwana ne cishinshimwe ca mitwi isanu ne ibili 12:1 mpaka 14:20 
\io1 Kayi lalembenga sha Indilo shisanu ne shibili shabukalu bwa Lesa 15:1 mpaka 16:18 
\io1 Cakonkapo Yohane lambanga sha Lesa mweshakabakomene balwani bakendi Kwilu 17:1 mpaka 20:15 
\io1 Cakupwililisha lambanga sha Kwilu kwalinolino ne cishi capanshi ca linolino ico cilakesanga kumapwililisho 22:21 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Mu libuku ili muli bintu Lesa mbyalayubulwila Yesu Klistu kwambeti ambile basebenshi bakendi, bintu byela kwinshika ca lino lino. Neco Klistu walatuma mungelo wakendi kuya kwambila Yohane musebenshi wakendi.  
\v 2 Yohane walamba byonse mbyalabona bilambanga sha mulumbe wa Lesa ne cancinencine ncalayubulwila Yesu Klistu.  
\v 3 Ukute colwe muntu labelengenga maswi abushinshimi ali mu libuku ili, kayi bakute colwe bantu balakutikinga maswi ne kwasunga. Cindi ca kwambeti bintu bitatike kwinshika cilipepi. 
\s1 Milumbe ku mibungano isanu ne ibili 
\p  
\v 4 Njame Yohane, ndalembelenga mibungano isanu ne ibili ili mu cimpansha ca Asiya. Luse ne lumuno kufuma kuli Lesa uyo walikubapo, ulipo kayi uyo lesanga, bibe ne njamwe. Luse ne lumuno kufuma kumishimu isanu ne ibili ili ku Cipuna ca Bwami bwa Lesa bibe ne njamwe.  
\v 5 Kayi luse ne lumuno kufuma kuli Yesu Klistu, kamboni washomeka bibe ne njamwe. Yesu emutanshi kupunduka kubafu walakoma lufu, endiye lendeleshenga bami ba pacishi capanshi. Walatusuna netulubula ku bwipishi ne milopa yakendi.  
\v 6 Nendi latubiki kuba bami ne beshimilumbo beshikusebensela Lesa, Baishi. Yesu Klistu apewe bulemu ne ngofu lelo ne masuba onse, Ameni!  
\v 7 Kamubonani, lesanga mumakumbi, uliyense nakamubone, ne bonse balamuyasa.Bantu bonse pacishi capanshi nibakamulile.Neco kacikabani motepelomo. 
\p Kamubonani, Yesu lesanga pamo ne makumbi. Bantu bonse nibakamubone, naboyo balikumuyasa nibakamubone. Bantu bamishobo yonse pacishi capanshi nibakalile cebo ca endiye. Ee, ici nicikenshike! Ameni.  
\v 8 Mwami Lesa wa ngofu shonse, uyo walikubako, ulipo kayi uyo lakesanga. Lambangeti, “Ame njame citatiko kayi njame mapwililisho.” 
\s1 Yohane labononga Klistu mu cimbonimboni 
\p  
\v 9 Njame Yohane washoma munenu, tulapengenga cebo ca Yesu Mwami wetu, uyo latupanga ngofu sha kupita mu mapensho. Ndalabikwa pa nsumbu ya Patimo cebo ca kukambauka mulumbe wa Lesa, ne cancinencine ico ncalayubulula Yesu.  
\v 10 Pa busuba bwa Mwami, Mushimu Uswepa walamfukata, kayi ndalanyumfwa maswi akompolola kunyuma kwakame, alikunyumfwiketi kulila kwa tolompita.  
\v 11 Kambeti, “Kolemba mulibuku bintu mbyolabononga, kayi watume ku mibungano isanu ne ibili ku Efenso ku Simuna ku Pegamo ku Tiyatila ku Salidisi ku Filadelufiya ne ku Lawodikeya.” 
\p  
\v 12 Mpondalacebuketi mbone walikwamba ne njame, ndalabona pakubika malampi asanu ne abili a golide.  
\v 13 Pakati pa byakubikapo malampi asa, palikuba naumbi walikuboneketi Mwana Muntu, walikuba wafwala mwinjila utali washika ku myendo kayi walikuba walikobeka cikwisa ca golide pa cali.  
\v 14 Mishishi ya kumutwi wakendi yalikuba tuu eti buluba, nambi eti mapepe ankobokobo, menso akendi alikuboneketi makalangasha a mulilo.  
\v 15 Myendo yakendi yalikubeketi cela cilafukutwanga pa muba, kayi maswi akendi alikunyumfwiketi kuwota kwa menshi angi.  
\v 16 Mucikasa cakendi cakululyo, walikuba wekata nyenyenshi shisanu ne shibili. Kayi mu mulomo wakendi, mwalafuma cibeshi calumata konse konse. Pa cinso cakendi palikubangileti lisuba lyanga pelu pa mutwi.  
\v 17 Mpondalamulangishisha, ndalawa panshi kumwendo yakendi eti muntu lafu. Neye walabika cikasa cakendi pali njame ne kwambeti, “Kotatina! ame njame citatiko ne mapwililisho.  
\v 18 Ndemuyumi! Ndalikuba wafwa, nomba lino kamubonani ndemuyumi kucindi camuyayaya, kayi nkute ngofu pa lufu ne pabantu bona mucishi cabafu.  
\v 19 Kolemba bintu mbyolabono, bilenshikinga pa cino cindi kayi ne byeti bikenshike kuntangu.  
\v 20 Lino ndapandululunga bintu mbyowabulanga kwinshiba cena, nyenyenshi shisanu ne shibili nshewalabona ku cikasa cakame ca ku lulyo, kayi ne pakubika malampi pasanu ne pabili a golide. Nyenyenshi shisanu ne shibili ni batangunishi ba mibungano isanu ne ibili, kayi pakubika malampi pasanu ne pabili a golide ni mibungano isanu ne ibili.” 
\s1 Maswi ku mubungano wa ku Efenso 
\c 2  
\p Maswi ku mubungano waku Efenso 1 Ku mutangunishi wa mubungano wa ku Efenso komulembeleti, “Nyumfwani maswi a uyo wekata nyenyenshi shisanu ne shibili mu cikasa cakendi ca kululyo ukute kwenda pakubika malampi pa golide pasanu ne pabili.” 
\s1 Mulumbe ku mubungano wa ku Efenso 
\p  
\v 1 Ku mutangunishi wa mubungano wa ku Efenso komulembeleti, “Uwu ni mulumbe ulafumunga kuli uyo wekata nyenyenshi shisanu ne shibili mu cikasa cakendi ca kululyo, ukute kwenda pakubika malampi pa golide pasanu ne pabili.  
\v 2 Ndibinshi mbyowensako, incito shakobe, kayi wapitanga mu mapensho nkokutebwelela kunyuma.Ndicisheti nkowela kwendela pamo ne muntu waipa. Bantu nabambi balalituntungeti ni batumwa, ulabelekeshenga ne kucaneti ni bandemishibili.  
\v 3 Wekalikana cali, ulapengelenga ame nsombi nkolabwelelenga kunyuma sobwe.  
\v 4 Nomba nikukabeco, ndakucana ne mulandu wakwambeti, nkonsunipo mbuli ncowalikunsuna pakutanguna.  
\v 5 Anuka mushinga ngowalawa, shiya bwipishi kayi utatike kwinsa caina ncowalikwinsa pakutanguna. Na ubule kushiya bwipishi, ndakesanga kusa kufunyapo pakubika lampi pakobe.  
\v 6 Nambi kulico, ucinsako caina pakwinga nkobisuni bilenshinga ba Nikolayi mbuli nenjame ncentabisunipo.”  
\v 7 “Uyo ukute matwi anyumfwe cilambanga Mushimu Uswepa ku mibungano!” “Beti bakakome ninkabasiminshe kulya ku cisepo cabuyumi cili mu libala lya Lesa.” 
\s1 Mulumbe ku mubungano waku Simuna 
\p  
\v 8 Ku mutangunishi wa mubungano wa ku Simuna komulembeleti, “Uwu mulumbe ulafumunga kuli wakutanguna kayi ne wakupwililisha. Uyo walafwa, nomba lino nimuyumi kayi.”  
\v 9 Ndainshi cena mapensho akobe, kayi ndicinsheti omupenshi, nikukabeco omubile. Ndibinshi byaipa byonse mbyobalakwambanga bantu balambangeti ni Bayuda nambi bantu bakunsa, abo bali mulikoto lya Satana.  
\v 10 Kotatina mapensho ngeshi ucane. Nyumfwani! Satana ulipepi kubasebenshesha balwani benu, kwambeti basunge nabambi ne kubawala mujele, kwambeti bamusunke. Nimukacane mapensho akatasha kwa masuba ali likumi. Nomba kamutakaleka kunshoma nambi bakamushine, pakwinga ninkamupe cilambo ca buyumi butapu.  
\v 11 “Ukute matwi anyumfwe cilambanga Mushimu Uswepa ku mibungano.” 
\p Lufu lwa tubili nteti bakakumane nalo bantu balakomonga ngofu sha bwipishi. 
\s1 Mulumbe ku mubungano wa ku Pegamo 
\p  
\v 12 Ku mutangunishi wa mubungano wa Pegamo komulembeleti, “Uwu ni mulumbe ulafumunga kuli wekata cibeshi calumata konse konse.  
\v 13 Ndicinsheti uko enkwabika cipuna cakendi cabwami. Nsombi mwashomeka kuli njame, muliya kutaya lushomo lwenu muli njame sobwe. Nambi mucindi kamboni wakame washomeka Antipa nkwalafwila uko kwalikwikala Satana.”  
\v 14 “Nomba nkuteko bintu bing'ana bya kutongauka. Muli njamwe nabambi balakonkelenga ciyisho ca Balamu, uyo walayisha Balaki kuwishila Baislayeli mu bwipishi bwa kulya byakulya byali kutwalwa ku tumbwanga ne kwinsa mubufule butambiki.”  
\v 15 Lino muli njamwe nabambi balakonkelenga ciyisho ca Banikolayi.  
\v 16 Lekani bwipishi lino! Na mubule kwinseco, ndesanga mwakufwambana kwisa kulwana nabo bantu abo ne cibeshi ceshi cikafume mu mulomo wakame. 
\p  
\v 17 “Ukute matwi anyumfwe cilambanga Mushimu Uswepa ku mibungano!” 
\p “Beti bakakome ninkabalyeshe mana asolekwa. Kayi umo ne umo ninkamupe libwe lituba lyalembwapo lina lya lino lino ndyateshipo muntu uliyense, nsombi ulinshi ni mwine lalitambulunga.” 
\s1 Mulumbe kumubungano waku Tayatila 
\p  
\v 18 Ku mutangunishi wa mubungano wa Tiyatila komulembeleti, “Uwu ni mulumbe ulafumunga ku Mwanendi Lesa ukute menso alabangilingeti cibilibili ca mulilo, ukute myendo ilanyekumungeti cela cilafukutwa.  
\v 19 Ndibwinshi cena buyumi bwakobe, lusuno lwenu kayi ne lushomo lwenu muli njame, ndicinshi ncemukute kunyamfwana umo ne munendi ne ncemukute kupita mu makatasho kwakubula kubwelela kunyuma. Ndicinshi kwambeti lino mulenshinga caina kupita pa cindi ncemwalanshoma.  
\v 20 Nomba nikukabeco, ndatongaukunga, pakwinga Yezebeli mutukashi ukute kulyambeti ni mushinshimi. Mulamulekenga kayisha biyisho bya bwepeshi ne kuwishila basebenshi bakame mu bufule butambiki ne mukulya byakulya bikute kubengwa ku tumbwanga.  
\v 21 Nomba ndamupako ka cindi kang'anowa kwambeti aleke kwinsa byaipa, nsombi lakananga kuleka bufule.”  
\v 22 Kamubonani, ninkamuwale pa bulili bwakendi mpoti akakolwele, pamo ne bonse mbwali kupombola nabo ninkabapenshewe, na babule kuleka kwinsa byaipa nendiye.  
\v 23 Ninkashine bonse balakonkonga biyisho byakendi, neco mibungano yonse nikenshibeti njame nkute kubona cilayeyenga bantu ne ncebalayandanga. Ninkape cisubulo kwelana ne bwipishi bwa muntu uliyense. 
\p  
\v 24 Mobambi uko ku Tiyatila nkamulakonkonga biyisho byaipa, nkamubinshi mbyobalambanga abo balamukonkonga mbyobalambangeti, “Mwine Satana mbyafumbika.” Ndamwambilingeti, nteti nkamutwikepo mutolo wa milawo naumbi wapita wa kwambeti,  
\v 25 pitilishani kushoma mwangofu muli njame kushikila nkese.  
\v 26 Beti bakakome mu nkondo iyi kayi beti bakapitilishe kwinsa ncondayandanga kushikila ku mapwililisho, ninkabapeko ngofu shakwendelesha mishobo yonse.  
\v 27 Nibakendeleshe mishobo ne nkoli ya cela, nibakapwayaule mishobo ya bantu mbuli ncebakute kutobaula nongo.  
\v 28 Mungofu shabwendeleshi shendalatambula kufuma kuli Bata. Nenjame ninkabape ntanda. 
\p  
\v 29 “Na mukute matwi nyumfwani cilambanga Mushimu wa Lesa ku mibungano!” 
\c 3  
\s1 Mulumbe ku mubungano wa ku Saladisi 
\p  
\v 1 Ku mutangunishi wa mubungano wa ku Saladisi komulembeleti, “Uwu ni mulumbe ulambwanga ne uyo ukute kwendelesha Mishimu isanu ne ibili ya Lesa, kayi ne nyenyenshi shisanu ne shibili. Ndishinshi incito shakobe, nambi bantu balambangeti omuyumi,nomba obe wafwa.”  
\v 2 Ndacaneti buyumi bwenu nkabwashikapo pa mwelo ngwalayandanga Lesa. Neco punduka mu tulo twakobe, yuminisha ico ncokute kacitana cifwililila.  
\v 3 Anuka ciyisho ncewalatambula, kayi ncewalanyumfwa. usunge shiya bwipishi bwakobe. Na ubule kupunduka, ndakesangeti kabwalala, nteti ukenshibe cindi nceti nkese.  
\v 4 Nomba nkobali bang'ana uko ku Saladisi babula kusafwanya minjila yabo, nibakende ne njame kabali bafwala minjila ituba tuu, pakwinga cabelela.  
\v 5 Abo beti bakakome bwipishi nibakafwale minjila ituba mbuli ili. Nteti nkafunyemo maina abo mu libuku lya buyumi. Ndakemananga pamenso a Bata ne bangelo ninkambeti, aba nibakame.  
\v 6 “Uyo ukute matwi anyumfwe cilambanga Mushimu Uswepa ku mibungano!” 
\s1 Mulumbe ku mubungano waku Filadelufiya 
\p  
\v 7 Ku mutangunishi wa mubungano wa ku Filadelufiya komulembeleti, “Uwu ni mulumbe ulafumunga ku muntu waswepa kayi wa ncine ncine, uyo ukute cakucalwisha mbuli ncalikukute mwami Dafeti, na lacalulu cishinga paliya wela kucicala sobwe, kayi na lacicala paliya wela kucicalula.  
\v 8 Incito shakobe ndishinshi, ndicinsheti ukute ngofu shing'ana. Ulakonkonga ciyisho cakame, kayi washomeka kuli njame. Ndacalula cishinga pantangu pakobe paliya wela kucicala sobwe.”  
\v 9 Konyumfwa! Pali bantu bali kulubasu lwa Satana, balalibepengeti ni Bayuda kakuli ntebo Bayuda, ninkalengesheti bakese bakasuntame mulimfwa lyakobe. Mpweshi bakenshibeti ndikusuni.  
\v 10 Pakwinga ulapitilishi kunyumfwila milawo yakame kwakubula kubwelela kunyuma, ne njame ninkakucingilishe mu cindi ca mapensho alesanga kwisa kusunka bantu bonse pa cishi capanshi.  
\v 11 Ndesanga lino lino. Ikatisha ca makasa abili ico ncokute kwambeti kapataba muntu eti akunyongomone cilambo.  
\v 12 Uliyense eshi akakome nakabe ntabo mu Ng'anda ya Lesa wakame, nteti bakafumemo. Ninkalembe lina lya Lesa wakame ne lya Yelusalemu wa lino lino uyo lakaselukunga kwilu kuli Lesa. Kayi nenjame ninkalembe lina lyakame lya lino lino palyendibo.  
\v 13 “Ukute matwi anyumfwe cilambanga Mushimu Uswepa ku mibungano!” 
\s1 Mulumbe ku Mubungano wa ku Lawodikaya 
\p  
\v 14 Kuli mutangunishi wa mubungano wa ku Laodikaya komulembeleti, “Uwu e mulumbe ulafumunga kuli uyo ukute kukwiweti, Ameni, kamboni washomeka kayi wa ncine ncine, citente ca byonse byalalengwa ne Lesa.  
\v 15 Ndicinshi ncolenshinga pakwinga ndicinsheti nkowatontola nambi kulungula, nsombi ndayandishishanga kwambeti ucanike ku lubasu lumo!  
\v 16 Nomba pakwinga wakasala nkowalungula nambi kutontola, nindikusanke!”  
\v 17 Ha! ulambangeti, omubile ntobe mupenshi, ukute byonse. Nomba ukute malele, omukandu kayi ukute kupesha nkumbo, uli matakosha kayi washipilwa.  
\v 18 Leka ndikupeko mano, kwesa uleko golide waswepa kuli njame kwambeti ube mubile. Kayi wise uleko cikwisa cituba nceti ufwalenga kwambeti kotaboneshanga matakosha eshikupesha nsoni. Kayi wise uleko mafuta akunana ku menso kwambeti ubonenga cena. 
\p  
\v 19 Nkute kukansa nekupa cisubulo bantu mbonsuni. Neco, koba wakangwabu leka bwipishi.  
\v 20 Konyumfwa! Ndemana pa cishinga ndakonkoshunga, uliyense lanyumfunga maswi akame ne kucalulako, ninkengile mung'anda ne kuya kulya pamo nendiye, neye nakalye pamo nenjame  
\v 21 Abo beti bakakome ninkabasuminishe kwambeti nabo bekale pa bipuna bya bulemu bili pambali pa cipuna cakame cabwendeleshi, mbuli ne njame ncendekala pa cipuna cabwendeleshi cili pambali pa cipuna ca bulemu ca Bata pakwinga ndalakoma.  
\v 22 “Ukute matwi anyumfwe cilambanga Mushimu Uswepa ku mibungano!” 
\c 4  
\s1 Cipuna ca Bwami ca Lesa 
\p  
\v 1 Pa cindici ndalabona cimboni mboni nacimbi, ndalabona cishinga ca kwilu cacaluka. Maswi alikunyumfwiketi kulila kwa tolompita ngondali kunyumfwa kamba kuli njameti, “Kwesa kuno ndikuleshe bintu byeti bitatike kwinshika panyuma pa ibi.”  
\v 2 Mushimu wa Lesa mpowalamfukata, ndalabona cipuna ca Bwami kwilu ne uyo walikuba wekalapo.  
\v 3 Uyo walikuba wekala pa cipuna cinso cakendi calikubeketi mabwe akute kukwiweti Yasipi ne Kolinali. Ico cipuna calikuba cashingulukwa ne nkongolo yabeketi mabwe akute kukwiweti Emalodi.  
\v 4 Cipuna cabwami ico calikuba cashingulukwa nebipuna nabimbi makumi abili ne bina apo palikuba pekala bamakulene bali makumi abili ne bana bafwala minjila ituba ne ngowani sha bwami.  
\v 5 Kubyasha kwali kufuma ku cipuna, nako kwilu kwalatatala ne kukunkuma. Pantangu pa cipuna palikuba malampi asanu ne abili alikubangila, iyi emishimu isanu ne ibili ikute kusebensela Lesa.  
\v 6 Kayi pantangu pa cipuna palikuboneketi lwenje lwabeketi gilasi lwalikubangileti libwe likute kukwiweti Kulistali. 
\p Pakati kati kushinguluka cipuna ca bwami cisa, palikuba bya buyumi bina byalikukute menso angi kuntangu ne kunyuma.  
\v 7 Cabuyumi cakutanguna calikuboneketi inkalamu, catubili eti ng'ombe, cabutatu calikukute cinso cilyeti muntu, kayi ca cina calikuboneketi cikumbula laulukunga mwilu.  
\v 8 Cili conse ca bya buyumi bina ibi, calikukute mapepe asanu ne limo alikukute menso paliponse mukati ne kunsa. Munshi ne mashiku kwakubula kulekesha bikute kabimbileti, 
\q1 “Waswepa, waswepa, 
\q1 waswepa ni Mwami Lesa wa Ngofu shonse, 
\q1 ewalikubako, euliko kayi elesanga.” 
\p  
\v 9 Bya buyumi ibi bina, bikute kwimbila nyimbo shabulemeneno shakulemekesha kayi ne kulumbanya uyo wekala pa cipuna muyumi kwamuyayaya.  
\v 10 Mpobyalikwimbila, bamakulene makumi abili ne bana, balawa panshi pantangu pa uyo wekala pa cipuna ne kumukambilila, uyo ukute buyumi bwamuyayaya. Kabawala ngowani shabo pantangu pa cipuna ca bwami kabambeti, 
\q1  
\v 11 “O Mwami Lesa wetu! 
\q1 Mwelela kupewa bulemeneno kulemekeshewa ne kushikayishiwa cebo ca ngofu shenu, 
\q1 Pakwinga mwalabumba bintu byonse, 
\q1 Kayi cebo ca kuyanda kwenu byonse mpobili ni biyumi.” 
\c 5  
\s1 Libuku ne Mwana Mbelele 
\p  
\v 1 Panyuma pakendi ndalabona libuku mu cikasa ca kululyo ca uyo walikuba wekala pacipuna ca bwami lyalembwa mukati ne kunsa, lyalikuba kayi lyadindwa ne bidindo bisanu ne bibili.\fig Libuku lyadindwa bidindo bisanu ne bibili|src="03 Seals.jpg" size="col" ref="5:1" \fig* 
\v 2 Kayi ndalabona mungelo ukute ngofu sha bwendeleshi kepusha mwakompolola, “Inga niyani welela kumatula cidindo ne kucalula libuku ili ne kubona bili mukati?”  
\v 3 Nomba paliya walacanika kwilu nambi pa cishi ca panshi nambi kwinshi ca cishi, walikukute ngofu sha kucalula libuku ne kubona bili mukati.  
\v 4 Ndalalila kwine pakuboneti paliya walikuba welela kucalula libuku ne kubona bili mukati.  
\v 5 Neco umo wa bamakulene basa walang'ambileti, “Kotalila. Kobona! Inkalamu ya mu mukowa wa Yuda, mushikululwa wa Dafeti, elakomo nkondo, neco ewelela kumatula bidindo ne kucalula libuku.” 
\p  
\v 6 Popelapo ndalabona Mwana Mbelele kali wemana pakati pacipuna ca bwami,kali washingulukwa ne bya buyumi bina ne bamakulene makumi abili ne bana. Mwana Mbelele walikuboneketi pali lamushini, walikukute meca asanu ne abili kayi ne menso asanu ne abili. Uku ekwambeti mishimu isanu ne ibili ya Lesa yatumwa mu cishi conse ca panshi.  
\v 7 Mwana mbelele walamanta libuku lisa lyalikuba mu cikasa ca kululyo ca usa walikuba wekala pa cipuna cabwami cisa.  
\v 8 Mpwalamanta libuku, bya buyumi bina ne bamakulene makumi abili ne bana balawa pantangu pa Mwana Mbelele. Umo ne umo walikukute kalumbu ne ndilo shadongomana shagolidi shesula twanunkila, uku ekwambeti, mipailo ya bantu ba Lesa.  
\v 9 Balikwimbila lwimbo lwalino lino, lulambangeti, 
\q1 “Njamwe mwelela kumanta libuku ne kumatula cidindo ne kulicalula. 
\q1 Pakwinga mwalashinwa, ne milopa yenu mwalaulila Lesa bantu ba mishobo, 
\q1 ne bishi ne milaka kayi ne bantu bankanda shapusanapusana, 
\q1  
\v 10 mulababiki pamo kuba mushobo wa bami ne beshimilumbo beshi kusebensela Lesa wetu, beti bakasebenselenga pano pa cishi ca panshi.” 
\p  
\v 11 Kayi ndalanyumfwa ne kubona bangelo bangi myanda myanda itabelengeke ne bya buyumi bina kayi ne bamakulene makumi abili ne bana kabali bashinguluka cipuna.  
\v 12 Kabembila mwakompolola lwimbo lulambangeti, 
\q1 “Mwana Mbelele walashinwa, 
\q1 ewelela kupewa bwendeleshi ne buboni ne mano 
\q1 ne ngofu ne kulemekeshewa ne bulemeneno kayi ne kushikaishiwe!” 
\p  
\v 13 Popelapo ndalanyumfwa byonse byalabumbilwa kwilu ne pa cishi ca panshi ne bya panshi pene pene, bya mu lwenje, byonse bikute buyumi kabimbileti, 
\q1 “Kuli uyo wekala pa cipuna 
\q1 ne Mwana Mbelele bashikaishiwe, 
\q1 balemekeshewe, bapewe 
\q1 bulemeneno ne ngofu kwamuyayaya.” 
\p  
\v 14 Bya buyumi bina byalakumbuleti “Ameni!” Basa bamakulene balasuntama ne kukambilila. 
\c 6  
\s1 Byando 
\p  
\v 1 Panyuma pakendi ndalabona Mwana Mbelele usa kamatula cando cakutanguna pa bidindo bisa bisanu ne bibili, kayi ndalanyumfwa cimo ca bya buyumi kacolobesheti kutatala kwa mfula kacambeti, “Kwesa!”  
\v 2 Mpondalalangishisha, ndalabona lihaki lituba. Walikuba watantapo walikukute buta, kayi walapewa ngowani ya bwami, walikuya kulangaula balwani kwambeti abakome.  
\v 3 Lino kayi Mwana Mbelele mpwalamatula cidindo ca tubili, ndalanyumfwa ca buyumi ca cibili naco kacambeti, “Kwesa!”  
\v 4 Lihaki nalimbi lyalabonekela, lifubela. Watantapo walapewa ngofu sha kuleta nkondo pa cishi ca panshi kwambeti bantu bashinanenga. Walapewa cibeshi cinene.  
\v 5 Mwana Mbelele mpwalamatula cidindo ca butatu, ndalanyumfwa cabuyumi ca butatu naco kacambeti, “Kwesa!” Ndalalangishisha kayi ndalabona lihaki lishipa. Watantapo walikukute bipimo bibili mu makasa.  
\v 6 Ndalanyumfwa maswi alikufuma pakati pa bya buyumi bina, alikwambeti, “Cikopo ca bunga bwa maila celane ne malipilo amuntu a pabusuba, kayi bikopo bitatu bya bunga bwa mancebele byelane ne malipilo a muntu a pabusuba. Nomba kotelekesha kononga bitondo byamaolifi nambi bya mavaini.” 
\p  
\v 7 Mwana Mbelele mpwalamatula cidindo ca cina, ndalanyumfwa cabuyumi ca cina kacambeti, “Kwesa!”  
\v 8 Ndalabona lihaki lyacisefu lyakoka. Watantapo walikukwiweti, Lufu, naco cishi ca bantu bafwa calikonka pepi. Walapewa ngofu shakushina cibela cimo ca bibela bina ca bantu ne banyama ku nkondo, kunsala kayi ne ku malwashi ne kubanyama.  
\v 9 Lino ibi mpobyalapwa Mwana Mbelele walamatula cidindo ca busanu, ndalabona mishimu ya bantu panshi pa nteme, balashinwa cebo ca kukambauka maswi a Lesa ne kwinshila bukamboni mwakushomeka.  
\v 10 Yalompololeti, “Mwami wa ngofu shonse waswepa kayi wakubinga! Nipakapite cindi citali cilyeconi ca kwisa kombolosha bantu pa cishi ca panshi ne kupa cisubulo abo balatushina?”  
\v 11 Bonse balapewa minjila ituba ne kubambileti, “Bapumwine kwa kacindi kang'ana kwambeti mpaka mwelo wacibelengelo ukakwane wa basebenshi banabo ne bashomeka banabo belela kushinwa mbuli naboyo ncebalashinwa.” 
\p  
\v 12 Kayi popelapo ndalabona Mwana Mbelele kamatula cidindo ca cisanu ne cimo. Lino kwalesa mutuntumo wa inshi, lisuba lyalashipeti cikwisa ca shilika, nawo mwenshi walafubeleti milopa.  
\v 13 Nyenyenshi shalalukumuka panshi eti cikute kullukumuka nkuyu shibesu ku citondo cilanyukanwanga ne lukupwe lwangofu.  
\v 14 Namo mwilu muma kumbi mwalapetwa petwa eti ncakute kupetwa mapepala. Milundu ne nsumbu shalafuma mposhalikuba.  
\v 15 Neco, bami bapacishi capanshi ne bendeleshi ne bamakulene ba nkondo ne bakute buboni, bakute ngofu, ne bantu bonse, basha pamo ne bonse ne abo babula kuba basha. Bonse nibakasolame mu maceni a mabwe mu milundu.  
\v 16 Nibakasenge milundu ne mabwe kwambeti, “Kamutufwekelelako mutusoleke katutaboneka ku menso a uyo wekala pa cipuna ne kubukalu bwa Mwana Mbelele!”  
\v 17 Ee, busuba buyosha bwa Lesa ne Mwana mbelele bwakupa cisubulo bulashiki, sena pali naba umo eti akabule kupewa cisubulo? 
\c 7  
\s1 Baislayeli bali 144,000 
\p  
\v 1 Mpobyalapwa ibi ndalabona bangelo bana kabali bemana mu mbasu shina sha cishi ca panshi, kabakanisha lukupwe mu mbasu shina eti kalutonda pa cishi, nambi pa lwenje nambi pa citondo cili conse.  
\v 2 Kayi ndalabona naumbi mungelo wali kufumina kucwe kakute cidindo ca Lesa muyumi. Walompolola ku bangelo bana basa, Lesa mbwalapa ngofu sha kononga cishi ne lwenje.  
\v 3 Mungeloyo walambeti, “Kamutononga cishi, nambi lwenje nambi bitondo, nanshi tudinde cishibisho pankumo pa basebenshi ba Lesa wetu.”  
\v 4 Neco ndalambilweti cibelengelo ca bantu baladindwa cishibisho ca Lesa pankumo, bali bina mwanda umo ne makumi ana nebina bina (144,000). Aba balafumunga mu mikowa likumi ne ibili ya ba Islayeli. 
\q1  
\v 5 Bina likumi ne bibili (12,000) Mu mukowa wa Yuda, 
\q1 bina likumi ne bibili mu mukowa wa Lubeni, 
\q1  
\v 6 bina likumi ne bibili mu mukowa wa Gadi. 
\q1 Bina likumi ne bibili mu mukowa wa Aseli, 
\q1 bina likumi ne bibili mu mukowa wa Nafitali, 
\q1 bina likumi ne bibili mu mukowa wa Manase. 
\q1  
\v 7 Bina likumi ne bibili mu mukowa wa Shimoni, 
\q1 bina likumi ne bibili mu mukowa wa Levi, 
\q1 bina likumi ne bibili mu mukowa wa Isakala. 
\q1  
\v 8 Bina likumi ne bibili mu mukowa wa Sebuloni, bina likumi ne bibili mu mukowa wa Yosefe, kayi 
\q1 ne bina likumi ne bibili mu mukowa wa Benjameni. 
\s1 Likoto linene litabelengeke 
\p  
\v 9 Mpobyalapwa ibi ndalabona likoto linene, muntu ndyela kubula kukonsha kulibelenga! Lilafumunga mu bantu ba nkanda shapusana, ne mishobo ne bishi kayi ne milaka, kabali bemana ncili pantangu pa cipuna ca Bwami ne pantangu pa Mwana Mbelele. Kabali bafwala minjila ituba kayi kabali bekata misampi ya tukunka mumakasa.  
\v 10 Balompololeti, “Lupulusho lulafumunga kuli Lesa wetu, wekala pa cipuna ca Bwami kayi ne ku Mwana Mbelele!”  
\v 11 Bangelo bonse balemana ncili, kushinguluka Cipuna ca Bwami pamo ne bamakulene ne bya buyumi bina. Balasuntama ne kukotamika binso byabo pantangu pa Cipuna ca Bwami ne kukambila Lesa kabambeti,  
\v 12 “Ameni! Kushikaishiwa, ne bulemeneno ne mano ne kulumbaisha ne kulemekesha ne bwendeleshi kayi ne ngofu bibe kuli Lesa wetu kwa muyayaya! Ameni!” 
\p  
\v 13 Umo pa bamakulene basa walanjipusheti, “Inga bantu bafwala minjila ituba aba nibani, kayi balafumunga kupeyo?” 
\p  
\v 14 Ndalamukumbuleti, “Nkambo njamwe mucinshi cena.” 
\p Neye walambeti, “Aba ebantu balapiti mu makatasho atambiki. Ebalacapa ne kuswepesha minjila yabo mu milopa ya Mwana Mbelele.”  
\v 15 Encebemanina ku Cipuna ca Bwami bwa Lesa 
\q1 ne kumusebensela munshi ne mashiku mu Ng'anda yakendi. 
\q1 Wekala pa cipuna ca Bwami 
\q1 nakekale nabo ne kubacinjilisha. 
\q1  
\v 16 Nteti bakanyumfwepo nsala nambi nyotwa, 
\q1 nambi kupya ne lubela lwakulungula lwa lisuba. 
\q1  
\v 17 Pakwinga Mwana Mbelele 
\q1 uli pakati kati pacipuna ca Bwami 
\q1 nakabe mwembeshi wabo. 
\q1 Nakabatangunine ku nsansa netulonga twa menshi eshikupa buyumi. 
\q1 Lesa nakabapukute misonshi yonse pamenso pabo. 
\c 8  
\s1 Mwana mbelele lamatulunga cidindo ca cisanu ne cibili 
\p  
\v 1 Mwana Mbelele mpwalakumatula cidindo ca cisanu ne cibili, kwilu konse kwalamwena tonto kwa cintimbi ca ola.  
\v 2 Ndalabona kayi bangelo basanu ne babili bemana pantangu pa Lesa kabapewa matolompita asanu ne abili. 
\p  
\v 3 Mungelo naumbi walesa kwimana pa nteme kakute cakutentelamo lubani, walapewa lubani lwinji kusankanya pa mipailo ya bantu ba Lesa, ne kwitwala pa nteme ya golide ili pantangu pa Cipuna ca Bwami.  
\v 4 Bwishi bwa lubani lwalikutentwa lwalasankana pamo ne mipailo ya bantu ba Lesa kufuma mu makasa a mungelo walikuba wemana pantangu pa Lesa. 
\p  
\v 5 Lino mungelo walamanta cakutentelamo lubani ne kucisusha makalangasha a mulilo wa panteme ne kwawala pa cishi ca panshi. Palaboneka kutatala ne kubyasha byasha ne mutuntumo wa inshi. 
\s1 Bangelo balalilishinga matolompita 
\p  
\v 6 Bangelo basa basanu ne babili balikukute matolompita asanu ne abili balalibambileti batatike kwalilisha. 
\p  
\v 7 Mungelo wakutanguna walalilisha tolompita yakendi. Imfula ya mabwe ne mulilo wasankana ne milopa yalapomokela pa cishi ca panshi. Mbasu shitatu sha cishi ca panshi, mbasu shitatu sha bitondo, kayi ne mila yamwemfu yonse yalapya. 
\p  
\v 8 Mungelo watubili walalilisha tolompita yakendi. Cintu calikuboneketi mulundu unene walikupya mulilo walawalwa mu lwenje. Mbasu shitatu sha lwenje shalasanduka milopa,  
\v 9 mbasu shitatu sha byabuyumi byalafwila mu lwenje, mbasu shitatu sha mato anene shalapasauka. 
\p  
\v 10 Mungelo wa citatu walalilisha tolompita yakendi. Lunyenyenshi lunene lwalikuboneketi lampi lwalalaka kwilu. Lwalalakila pa mbasu shitatu sha milonga ne pa tusensa twa menshi.  
\v 11 Lina lya lunyenyenshi ulu ni “Kulula”. Mbasu shitatu sha menshi shalalula, bantu bangi balanwa menshi balafwa pakwinga alalula. 
\p  
\v 12 Mungelo wa cina walalilisha tolompita yakendi. Mbasu shitatu sha lisuba, mwenshi ne nyenyenshi byonse byalafwa cakwinseti byalalilwa kumunikila mbasu shitatu sha cindi. Nkakwalaba lumwi mu mbasu shitatu sha cindi ca munshi, kayi mbasu shitatu sha cindi ca mashiku. 
\p  
\v 13 Kandicilangishisha, ndalabona ne kunyumfwa cikumbula walikuluka mwilu mu mulenga lenga kompololeti, “Malele! Malele! Malele ku bantu bekala pa cishi ca panshi cebo ca bangelo batatu batana balilisha matolompita abo!” 
\c 9  
\p  
\v 1 Neye mungelo wa cisanu walalilisha tolompita yakendi. Ndalabona lunyenyenshi lwalesa kuwila panshi, kayi lwalapewa cakucalwisha ku cisengu citali.  
\v 2 Lunyenyenshi lusa mpolwalacalula ku cisengu, mwalapula bwishi bulyeti bwishi bwa bufuni bunene, lisuba ne mwilu byonse byalashipa cebo ca bwishi bwalafuma mu cisengu.  
\v 3 Mubwishi mwalapula bisoshi byalesula cishi conse ca panshi, kayi byalapewa ngofu shilyeti shikute nkalang'ongo.  
\v 4 Bisoshi ibyo balabyambileti, kabitononga mila, nambi bitondo nambi mumena uli wonse, nsombi bantu babula cishibisho ca Lesa cadindwa pa nkumo shabo.  
\v 5 Ibi bisoshi nkabyalasuminishiwa kushina bantu, nsombi kubapensha kwa myenshi isanu. Bululu bwa kupenshewa uko kwalikubeti bululu bwa kulumwa kwa nkalang'ongo.  
\v 6 Mukati mwa myenshi isanu iyo bantu nibakalangaule cela kubashina, nsombi nteti cikacanike sobwe. Nibakayande kufwa, nsombi nalo lufu nilukabafwambe. 
\p  
\v 7 Bisoshi byalikuboneketi mahaki alibambila nkondo, pa mitwi yabyo palikuba byalikuboneketi ngowani sha golide, kayi kucinso byalikuboneketi cinso ca muntu.  
\v 8 Byalikukute mishishi ilyeti ya batukashi, meno abyo alikubeti meno a nkalamu.  
\v 9 Byali byabyo byali cinjilishiwa ne bintu byalikuboneketi byela byali kusebenseshewa pa nkondo, kulila kwa mapepe akendi kwalikubeti mang'ola angi alakwelewanga ne mahaki alafwambilinga ku nkondo.  
\v 10 Mu micila ya bisoshibyo emwalikuba bululu bulyeti bwa nkalang'ongo, micila yabyo eyalikukute ngofu ya kupensha bantu kwa myenshi isanu.  
\v 11 Bikute mwami ukute kubyendelesha, uyu emungelo ukute ngofu pa cisengu citali. Mu Cihebeli lina lyakendi ni Abadoni, mu Cigiliki lina lyakendi ni Apolyoni. Lilapandululungeti, “Shikushina.” 
\p  
\v 12 Malele akutanguna alapiti, nomba kayi kulashala malele abili alesanga. 
\p  
\v 13 Lino mungelo wa cisanu ne umo neye walalilisha tolompita yakendi. Ndalanyumfwa maswi kufuma ku mbasu shina sha nteme ya golide yalikuba pantangu pa Lesa.  
\v 14 Awo maswi alikwambila mungelo wa cisanu ne umo walikukute tolompita kambeti, “Sungulula bangelo bana basungwa pa mulonga unene wa Filate!”  
\v 15 Neye mungelo wacisanu ne umo walabasungulula basa bangelo bana, kwambeti benga bashine mbasu shitatu sha bantu bonse. Abo bangelo, Lesa walababambila ola, busuba, mwenshi kayi ne caka cakwinseco.  
\v 16 Kayi walang'ambila cibelengelo ca makoto abashilikali batanta pa mahaki ankondo ali myanda ibili ya bina.  
\v 17 Mu cimboni mboni, ndalabona mahaki ne batantapo balikuba bafwala byakulicingilisha bya cela byafubeleti mulilo, ne bya shipuluka kayi ne byakateshi eti sulufule. Mitwi ya mahaki yalikubeti mitwi ya nkalamu, mulilo ne bwishi kayi byalikufuma mu milomo.  
\v 18 Mbasu shitatu sha mushobo wa bantu shalafwa ku malwashi atatu, awa ni mulilo ne bwishi kayi ne sulufule, byalikufuma mu milomo ya mahaki.  
\v 19 Pakwinga ngofu sha mahaki awa, shalikuba mu milomo kayi ne mu micila yasho. micila yasho yalikubeti mitwi ya njoka kwambeti ipenshe bantu. 
\p  
\v 20 Bantu balashala balabula kufwa ku malwashi awa, baliya kuleka kwinsa byaipa byakukambilila bintu mbyebalabamba ne makasa abo.Baliya kuleka kukambilila mishimu yaipa, tumbwanga twa golide, twasilifa ne twamukuba ne twamabwe kayi ne twabitondo. Utu tonse nkatubono, nkatunyumfu nambi kwenda.  
\v 21 Bantu aba baliya kulapa bwipishi bwakushinana umo ne munendi, nambi kuleka buloshi, nambi kuleka bufule butambiki, nambi bukabwalala. 
\c 10  
\s1 Mungelo ne kalibuku 
\p  
\v 1 Kayi ndalabona naumbi mungelo wangofu kaseluka kwilu, kali wafungailwa mumakumbi ne nkongolo kaili yamushinguluka ku mutwi. cinso cakendi calikuboneketi kumunika kwa lisuba ne myendo yakendi yalikubeti ntabo shilabangilinga mulilo.  
\v 2 Kayi walikukute kalibuku mu makasa kacaluka. Walikuba watalamana, mwendo wakululyo kali walyata pa lwenje, wa cipiko kali walyata pa mutunta,  
\v 3 maswi akendi akompolola alanyumfwiketi kubuluma kwa nkalamu. Mpwalapwisha, nako kutatala kusanu ne kubili kwalakumbula mwakubuluma.  
\v 4 Kutatala mpokwalapwa kwamba, ndalayandeti nembe mbyondalabona ne kunyumfwa, nomba ndalanyumfwa maswi kwilu akwambeti, “Soleka bilamba kutatala kwa tusanu ne tubili, kotabilemba sobwe.” 
\p  
\v 5 Usa mungelo ngondalabona kali walyata pa lwenje kayi ne pa mutunta, walemanika cikasa cakendi cakulyo kutondeka kwilu  
\v 6 ne kulumbila pa Lina lya Lesa wamuyayaya, uyo walalenga kwilu ne cishi ca panshi ne lwenje kayi ne byonse bilimo. Mungeloyo walambeti, “Nteti pakapite cindi citali sobwe!  
\v 7 Lino mungelo wa tusanu ne tubili alilisha tolompita yakendi, Lesa nakakwanilishe bubambo bwakendi bwasolekwa, mbwalambila basebenshi bakendi bashinshimi.” 
\p  
\v 8 Lino maswi ngondalanyumfwa kwilu kayi alamba kuli njameti, “Koya umante kalibuku kasa kacaluka kali mu makasa a mungelo walyata pa lwenje ne pa mutunta.” 
\p  
\v 9 Ndalaya ku mungelo kuya kumusenga kalibuku. Neye walang'ambileti, “Kamante ukalye, mulibunda nukanyumfwe kulula, nomba mukanwa nukanyumfwe kwineti bwiki.” 
\p  
\v 10 Ndalakamanta kalibuku kufuma mumakasa akendi ne kukalya, mukanwa kalanyumfwika kwineti bwiki. Nomba mpondalakamina ndalanyumfwa kulula mulibunda.  
\v 11 Popelapo ndalambilweti, “Koya ukambauke kayi mulumbe wa Lesa ku mishobo ne kubishi ne kubantu ba nkanda shapusana, ne milaka kayi ne ku bami bangi.” 
\c 11  
\s1 Bakamboni babili 
\p  
\v 1 Panyuma pakendi, ndalapewa katondo kalikuboneketi litete lyakupimisha, ne kung'ambileti, “Koya upime Ng'anda ya Lesa ne nteme kayi ubelenge bantu balakambililinga mu Ng'anda.  
\v 2 Nomba kotaya upime lubuwa, pakwinga lulapewa ku bantu batamwinshi Lesa beti bakaulyataule munshi uswepa kwa myenshi makumi ana ne ibili.  
\v 3 Ninkatume bakamboni bakame babili bafwala masankunya beti bakakambauke mulumbe wa Lesa mu masuba ali cina cimo ne myanda ibili ne makumi asanu ne limo.” 
\p  
\v 4 Bakamboni babili e bitondo bibili bya maolifi ne malampi abili ali pantangu pa Mwami lendeleshenga cishi capanshi.  
\v 5 Na mulwani welekesha kubalinga, mukanwa mwabo nimukafume mulilo weshi ukabashine balwani, uliyense eshakelekeshe kubalinga nakafwe munshila imo imo ilico.  
\v 6 Bakute ngofu shakucala kwilu kwambeti imfula kaitaloka pa cindi ncebalakambaukunga mulumbe wa Lesa. Bakute ngofu shakusandula menshi kuba milopa. Kayi bakute ngofu sha kuleta malwashi apusana pusana pacishi capanshi pa cindi ncebalayandanga. 
\p  
\v 7 Bakapwisha kukambauka mulumbe bakamboni babili, cinyama ico cilapulunga mu cisengu citali ne kwisa kulwana nabo. Nicikabakome ne kubashina,  
\v 8 bitumbi byabo nibikabenga byonekwa munshila sha mu munshi unene mwalapopwa Mwami. Lina lya mansendelele lya munshi uwo ni Sodomu nambi Injipito.  
\v 9 Bantu ba mubishi byonse ne mishobo yonse ne milaka yonse, kayi ne bantu ba nkanda shapusana, nibakebelenga bitumbi ibyo kwa masuba atatu ne cintimbwi, nteti bakasuminisheti bibikwe mu manda.  
\v 10 Pa cishi capanshi bantu nibakakondwe cebo ca lufu lwa aba bantu babili. Nibakasekelele ne kutumishilana bintu, pakwinga bashinshimi babili basa balapensha pa cishi capanshi.  
\v 11 Nomba panyuma pa masuba atatu ne cintimbwi, muya weshikupa buyumi walafuma kuli Lesa walabengila. Balapatamuka ne kwimana, neco, bantu balababona balatina kwine. 
\p  
\v 12 Lino bashinshimi babili basa balanyumfwa liswi lyali kompolola kwilu eti, “Kamwisani kwilu kuno!” Balwani babo kabacebelela, balo balanyamuka kuya kwilu mu likumbi.  
\v 13 Pacindi copeleco kwalesa mutuntumo unene cakwinseti ng'anda imo pa manda ali likumi onse mumunshi alawa. Kayi bantu bina bisanu ne bibili (7,000) Balafwa ne mutuntumo. Balashalapo balatina, balashikaisha bukulene bwa Lesa wa kwilu. 
\p  
\v 14 Malele atubili alapiti, nsombi kulesanga ca lino lino kayi malele atutatu! 
\s1 Tolompita ya cisanu ne cibili 
\p  
\v 15 Mungelo wa cisanu ne cibili mpwalalilisha tolompita yakendi, kwilu kwalanyumfwika maswi akompolola alikwambeti, “Lino ngofu shakwendelesha cishi capanshi shilapewa mu makasa a Mwami wetu ne Klistu Wananikwa wakendi, endiyeti endeleshenga kwa muyayaya!”  
\v 16 Bamakulene makumi abili ne bana bekala pa bipuna bwa bwami pantangu pa Lesa balakotamika byeni ne kukambilila Lesa  
\v 17 kabambeti, 
\q1 “Mwami Lesa Wangofu shonse omwalikubako kayi omuliko!Tulamulumbunga 
\q1 Pakwinga mulamanta ngofu shinene kayi mulatatiki kulela! 
\q1  
\v 18 Bantu batamwinshi Lesa balakalala, nomba cindi ca bukalu bwenu cilashiki, 
\q1 cakwambeti bafwa bomboloshewe. 
\q1 Cindi cilashiki cakupa cilambo kuba basebenshi benu bashinshimi, 
\q1 ne bantu benu bonse, ne bonse balamupanga bulemu bamakulene ne batwanike. 
\q1 Cindi cilashiki ca kononga balonongonga cishi!” 
\p  
\v 19 Ng'anda ya Lesa yalacaluka kwilu, Libokoshi lya Cipangano lyalaboneka mu Ng'anda ya Lesa. Popelapo kwalaba kubyasha ne nsakamwenge ne kutatala kwa mfula ne mutuntumo wa inshi kayi ne mfula ya mabwe. 
\c 12  
\s1 Mutukashi ne shi nshimwe 
\p  
\v 1 Lino kayi cingashilo cinene ciyosha calaboneka mwilu. Kwalaboneka mutukashi walikuba wafwala lisuba, walikuba wekala kali walyata myendo yakendi pa mwenshi, ku mutwi walikuba wafwala cishoti ca bwami cikute nyenyenshi likumi ne shibili.  
\v 2 Walikukute libunda, nomba mutukashuyo mpwalikuba pepi kutumbuka, walikulila cebo cakubabwa kwa pakutumbuka. 
\p  
\v 3 Lino kayi cingashilo nacimbi calaboneka mwilu. Ndalabona cishinshimwe cinene calikukute mitwi isanu ne ibili ne meca likumi kayi ne tushoti tusanu ne tubili twa bwami ku mutwi umo ne umo.  
\v 4 Mucila waco walakulumuna mbasu shitatu sha nyenyenshi mwilu ne kushiwala pa cishi capanshi. Cishinshimwe ico calatankamana kuntangu pepi ne mutukashi kwambeti atumbukowa cimulye mwana.  
\v 5 Usa mutukashi walatumbuka mwana mutuloba, eshakendeleshe mishobo yonse ne nkoli ya cela. Nomba mwanoyo walasompolwa ne kutwalwa kuli Lesa kuya kwikala pa cipuna cakendi ca bwami.  
\v 6 Neye mutukashi walafwambila ku cinyika, uko Lesa nkwalamubambila musena wakumulelelako kwa masuba cina cimo ne myanda ibili ne makumi asanu ne limo. 
\s1 Mungelo lalwananga ne Shinshimwe 
\p  
\v 7 Lino nkondo yalabalamuka kwilu. Mikayeli ne bangelo bakendi balalwana ne Shinshimwe, nendi Shinshimwe walikuba ne bangelo bakendi balalwanisha,  
\v 8 nomba Shinshimwe ne bangelo baco balakomwa, nkabalasuminishiwa kwikala mumusena wabo kwilu.  
\v 9 Cishinshimwe cinene calawalwa panshi, Shinshimwe wakaindi mwipishi ukute kukwiweti Satana, Muyungaushi wacishi capanshi conse. Balaciwala pa cishi capanshi pamo ne bangelo bakendi.  
\v 10 Pa cindi copeleco, ndalanyumfwa liswi lyakompolola kwilu akwambeti, 
\q1 Lino Lesa latupulushu! 
\q1 Lesa laleshe ngofu shakendi sha Bwami! 
\q1 Lino neye Wananikwa 
\q1 laleshe bwendeleshi bwakendi! 
\q1 Pakwinga usa wemananga pa menso a Lesa wetu, 
\q1 Wabepeshelanga banse betu pamenso a Lesa munshi ne mashiku 
\q1 lawalwa pa cishi capanshi. 
\p  
\v 11 Banse betu balamukomo 
\q1 cebo ca milopa ya Mwana Mbelele 
\q1 kayi ne cancine ncine ncebali kukambauka. 
\q1 Balikuba balibambila kuyaba buyumi bwabo pacindi ncebali kulangana ne lufu. 
\q1  
\v 12 “Neco kokondwa obe kwilu, ne mwense 
\q1 mwekala kwiluko! Nsombi malele kuli 
\q1 njamwe mwekala pa cishi capanshi ne pa lwenje! 
\q1 Muyungaushi, lesa uko panshi kulinjamwe, wesula ne bukalu pakwinga 
\q1 ucinsheti kacindi nikang'ana kalamushalili.” 
\p  
\v 13 Lino cishinshimwe mpocalenshibeti cilawalwa pa cishi capanshi, calatatika kukonka usa mutukashi walatumbuka mwana mutuloba.  
\v 14 Mutukashuyo walapewa mapepe abili alyeti acikumbula munene, kwambeti acikonshe kuluka kuya ku musena wakendi ku cinyika. Nkwalakalelwa cena kwa byaka bitatu ne cintimbwi kuyuba cishinshimwe cisa.  
\v 15 Lino cishinshimwe pakukonka mutukashi calapomona menshi angi mu mulomo waco alabeti mulonga kwambeti mutukashi usa enga ne menshi.  
\v 16 Nomba cishi capanshi calamunyamfwa mutukashi, calacaluka ne kumina menshi ngocalapomona cishinshimwe mu mulomo waco.  
\v 17 Ici ecalapesheti cishinshimwe cikalale cikamba ne mutukashi usa, neco calaya kulwana ne banabendi mutukashi kayi ne bantu bonse balanyumfwilinga milawo ya Lesa abo bashoma cancinencine calayubululwa ne Yesu.  
\v 18 Nomba cinjoka calakemana mulombe lwa lwenje. 
\c 13  
\s1 Binyama bibili 
\p  
\v 1 Kayi ndalabona cinyama kacitumpunuka mu lwenje, calikukute meca likumi ne mitwi isanu ne ibili. Pa lica lili lyonse palikuba ngowani, kayi pamutwi uliwonse palikuba pa lembwa lina lya kusebanya Lesa.  
\v 2 Ico cinyama calikubeti kankonongo, myendo yalikubeti ya malama kayi mulomo walikubeti wa nkalamu. Cishinshimwe cisa calayaba ngofu yaco ne cipuna kayi ne bwendeleshi ku cinyama.  
\v 3 Mutwi umo wa cinyama walikuboneketi cilonda cinene cakufwa naco, nsombi cilondeco calapola, palashalowa mubata. Bantu bonse pa cishi capanshi balikukonkela cinyama balakankamana.  
\v 4 Muntu uli yense walikukambilila cishinshimwe cisa, pakwinga ecalapa bwendeleshi kucinyama. Kayi naco cinyama balikucikambilila, pakwambeti, “Inga niyani welaneti cinyama? Inga niyani sena wela kulwana naco?” 
\p  
\v 5 Cinyama calasuminishiwa kwamba maswi akutwanga ne kusampula Lesa. Calasuminishiwa kuba ne ngofu sha bwendeleshi kwa myenshi makumi ana ne ibili.  
\v 6 Calatatika kutukana Lesa ne lina lyakendi ne musena nkwakute kwikala kayi ne bonse bakute kwikala kwilu.  
\v 7 Calasuminishiwa kulwana ne bantu ba Lesa ne kubakoma, kayi calapewa ngofu sha bwendeleshi pa mishobo yonse ne bishi byonse ne milaka yonse kayi ne pa bantu ba nkanda shapusana shonse.  
\v 8 Bantu bangi bekala cishi capanshi nibakacikambilile cinyama ico. Aba ebantu balabula kulembwa mulibuku lyabuyumi. Nomba abo bakute maina alalembwa mu libuku lya buyumi lya Mwana Mbelele kacitana cilengwa cishi, nteti bakacikambilile. 
\p  
\v 9 “Na mukute matwi nyumfwani!” 
\q1  
\v 10 “Uyo welela kwikatwa busha 
\q1 nakaikatwe busha.” 
\q1 “Uyo welela kufwa ku cibeshi, cakubinga 
\q1 nakafwe ku cibeshi.” 
\p Bantu ba Lesa bela kwikalika cali ne kuba ne lushomo. 
\p  
\v 11 Kayi ndalabona nacimbi cinyama calikufumbuka panshi. Calo calikukute meca abili alyeti meca a mwana mbelele, nomba calikwambeti cishinshimwe.  
\v 12 Calo calikukute ngofu shonse shabwendeleshi bwa cinyama cakutanguna cisa. Calikukakatisha cishi capanshi ne bantu bonse mucishi capanshi eti bakambililenga cisa cinyama cakutanguna calikukute mubata wa cilonda.  
\v 13 Cinyama ca cibili ici calensa bintu bingi bikankamanisha, calaleta mulilo pa cishi capanshi kufuma mwilu bantu bonse kabebelela.  
\v 14 Ici cinyama cacibili calabepa bantu pacishi capanshi, pakwinsa bintu bikankamanisha pakusebensesha ngofu nshecalapewa ne cinyama cakutanguna. Calabambileti babambe cikoshano ca cinyama cisa calabula kufwa mpocalayaswa cibeshi, nsombi calapitilisha kuba ciyumi.  
\v 15 Cinyama cacibili balacisuminisha kufubaila muya waco mucikoshano ca cinyama cakutanguna cisa, kwambeti cikonshe kwamba ne kushina bantu bonse balakananga kucikambilila.  
\v 16 Ici cinyama calakakatisha bantu bonse, batwanike ne bamakulene, bakute buboni ne babula buboni, basha kayi ne basunguluka kwambeti badindwe cishibisho pa cikasa ca kululyo nambi pa nkumo.  
\v 17 Paliya muntu wela kula nambi kulisha kali wabula cishibisho ico. Ici cishibisho cilemanininga lina lya cinyama, nambi cibelengelo ca lina lyaco. 
\p  
\v 18 Pano epali mano. Muntu wacenjela wela kwinshiba mwine bupandulushi bwa cibelengelo ca cinyama, pakwinga cibelengelo ca 666 cilemanininga lina lya muntu. 
\c 14  
\s1 Yohane labononga Mwana Mbelele pa mulundu wa Siyoni 
\p  
\v 1 Mpondalangishisha, ndalabona Mwana mbelele kali wemana pa mulundu wa Siyoni pamo ne bantu bali bina mwanda umo ne makumi ana ne bina. Abo balalembwa pa nkumo lina lya Mwana Mbelele kayi ne lina lya Baishi.  
\v 2 Kayi ndalanyumfwa liswi kwilu alikunyumfwiketi kuwota kwa menshi angi, kayi ne kutatala kwa mfula. Kayi eti bantu balombonga tulumbu.  
\v 3 Bantu basa balemana ku Cipuna ca Bwami pamo ne bya buyumi bina kayi ne bamakulene, balikwimbila lwimbo lwa linolino. Lwalikubula kwishibikwa ne muntu uliyense, nsombi bali bina mwanda umo ne bina makumi ana ne bina. Aba ebonka balaulwa pa cishi capanshi.  
\v 4 Ebantu balabula kulisafwanya ne batukashi. Baswepa eti ncebabele balindu batamwishi mutuloba. Bakute kukonkelowa nkwalenga Mwana Mbelele. Aba ebalaulwa pacishi capanshi kwambeti babe bantu batanshi kubengwa mulumbo kuli Lesa ne kuli Mwana Mbelele.  
\v 5 Ebantu balabula ku bepapo, kayi babula kampenda. 
\s1 Maswi abangelo batatu 
\p  
\v 6 Kufumapo ndalabona naumbi mungelo walikuluka mwilu kakute Mulumbe Waina utapu wakukambaukila bantu pa cishi capanshi ba nkanda shapusana shonse ne mishobo yonse ne milaka yonse kayi ne bishi byonse.  
\v 7 Mungeloyo walikompololeti, “Lemekeshani Lesa ne kumushikaisha bukulene bwakendi! Pakwinga cindi cakendi ca kombolosha muntu uliyense cilashiki. Musuntamineni walalenga kwilu ne cishi capanshi ne lwenje kayi ne tusensa twa menshi!” 
\p  
\v 8 Mungelo wa cibili walikukonkela mungelo mutanshi walikambeti, “Lau! Babulo munene, lau! Walikunwisha bantu waini, waini walula wa nyotwa yabufule bwakendi.” 
\p  
\v 9 Kayi mungelo wa citatu walabakonkela basa bangelo babili balatanguna, neye kompololeti, “Uliyense lakambililinga cinyama kayi ne mukoshano waco ne kuba ne cishibisho pa nkumo nambi pa cikasa,  
\v 10 nakanweko waini wabukalu bwakendi Lesa, waini wabula kusankanyako menshi ngweshi akapomwene mu nkomeshi ya bukalu bwakendi! Kayi nibakapenge ne mulilo ne sulufule, bangelo baswepa pamo ne Mwana Mbelele kabebelela.  
\v 11 Kayi bwishi bwa kupenshewa kwabo nibukasukumenga kwamuyayaya. Abo balakambililinga cinyama ne mukoshano waco, kayi uliyense walatambulako cishibisho ca lina lyaco nteti akapumwine munshi ne mashiku.” 
\p  
\v 12 “Bantu ba Lesa balanyumfwilinga Milawo yakendi, ne kushoma muli Yesu belela kwikalika cali.” 
\p  
\v 13 Kayi ndalanyumfwa liswi kwilu kalyambeti, “Ici kocilemba. Bakute colwe bantu balafunga kabali bashoma Lesa, kutatika pa cindi cino kuya kuntangu!” 
\p Mushimu wa Lesa ulambangeti, “Ee, balekeni benga bapumwine ku ncito shabo nshebali kusebensa, pakwinga nibakapewe cilambo pa ncito nshebali kwinsa.” 
\s1 Cindi ca kutebula cilashiki 
\p  
\v 14 Mpondalalangishisha, ndalabona likumbi lyatuba tuu. Apo pa likumbi palikuba pekala walikuboneketi Mwana Muntu wafwala ngowani ya Bwami ya golide ku mutwi, kakute cijekeshi calumata mu makasa.  
\v 15 Naumbi mungelo walapula mu Ng'anda ya Lesa kwilu kambila usa wekala pa likumbi eti, “Kotatikako kutebula ne cijekeshi cakobe, cindi cakutebula cilashiki, bishango pa cishi capanshi bilakomo kwambeti bitebulwe.”  
\v 16 Usa walikuba wekala pa likumbi kuyangula bishango pa cishi capanshi ne cijekeshi, kayi bishango pa cishi capanshi byalatebula. 
\p  
\v 17 Kayi naumbi mungelo walapula mu Ng'anda ya Lesa kwilu, neye wali kukute cijekeshi calumata. 
\p  
\v 18 Kayi naumbi mungelo walikukute ngofu sha kwendelesha mulilo, walapula pa nteme kabilikisha ku mungelo usa walikukute cijekeshi eti, “Kosebensesha cijekeshi cakobe uyangule minyansa mumabala a pacishi capanshi pakwinga minyansa ilakomo cena.”  
\v 19 Neco usa mungelo walayangula bisepo bya minyansa pa cishi capanshi, ne kubiwala mucisengu mwakutyanina bukalu bunene bwa Lesa.  
\v 20 Bisepo bya minyansa balabityanina mucisengu calikuba kunsa kwa munshi, mpobalabilyataula mwalatyanika milopa yalasanduka kuba mulonga utali wapita myanda itatu ya makilomita, kayi yashika mamita abili. 
\c 15  
\s1 Bangelo ne malwashi akupwililisha 
\p  
\v 1 Kayi mpondalalanga kwilu, ndalabona cingashilo nacimbi cinene kayi ciyosha. Bangelo basanu ne babili bakute malwashi asanu ne abili, malwashi awa emapwililisho abukalu bwa Lesa.  
\v 2 Kayi ndalabona cintu calikuboneketi lwenje lwa gilasi lwasankana ne mulilo. Kayi ndalabona bantu kabali bemana pepi ne lwenje lwa gilasi balakoma cinyama ne mukoshano waco ne cibelengelo ca lina lyaco.kabali bekata tulumbu ntwalabapa Lesa,  
\v 3 balikwimbila lwimbo lwa Mose musebenshi wa Lesa ne lwimbo lwa Mwana Mbelele lwakwambeti, 
\q1 “Amwe Lesa wa ngofu shonse, 
\q1 ncito shenu nishinene kayi shikute kuyosha! 
\q1 Amwe Mwami wa bishi byonse, 
\q1 nshila shenu shololoka kayi 
\q1 ni sha ncinencine! 
\q1  
\v 4 Niyani wela kubula kumutina Mwami? 
\q1 Niyani wela kukana kwamba sha bukulene bwenu? 
\q1 Amwe njamwe mwenka mwaswepa. 
\q1 Bantu mubishi byonse nibakese nibakamukambilile, 
\q1 pakwinga micito yenu yalulama 
\q1 kayi bonse nibakaibone.” 
\p  
\v 5 Calakonkapo, ndalabona ng'anda ya Lesa kwilu kaili yacaluka, mukati mwakendi mwalikuba Tente ya cipangano ca Lesa.  
\v 6 Basa bangelo basanu ne babili balikukute malwashi asanu ne abili balapula mu Ng'anda ya Lesa kabali bafwala byabeka, kabali balisunga lamba wa golide pa cali.  
\v 7 Cimo ca bya buyumi bina calapa bangelo basanu ne babili ndilo shafongomana shisanu ne shibili shesula bukalu bwa Lesa muyumi kwa muyayaya.  
\v 8 Ng'anda ya Lesa yalesula bwishi bwa bulememneno ne ngofu sha Lesa cakwinseti paliya walacikonsha kwingilamo, mpaka bangelo basanu ne babili bakapwishe kwitila malwashi asanu ne abili. 
\c 16  
\s1 Indilo sha bukalu bwa Lesa 
\p  
\v 1 Lino ndalanyumfwa liswi mu Ng'anda ya Lesa lyalikwambila bangelo basanu ne babili, “Kamuyani mwitile ndilo shisanu ne shibili sha bukalu bwa Lesa pa cishi capanshi!” 
\p  
\v 2 Wakutanguna waletila ndilo pa cishi capanshi. Bonse balikukute cishibisho ca cinyama ne balikukambilila mukoshano waco, balaba ne bilonda bishikubaba ciyosha. 
\p  
\v 3 Mungelo wacibili waletila ndilo yakendi pa lwenje. Menshi alasanduka milopa ilyeti ya muntu wafwa, kayi bya buyumi bya mu menshi byonse byalafwa. 
\p  
\v 4 Nendi mungelo wacitatu waletila ndilo yakendi pa milonga ne pansansa, kayi menshi alasanduka milopa.  
\v 5 Kayi ndalanyumfwa mungelo wali kwendelesha menshi kambeti, “Lombolosho lwenu lwalulama omulipo, kayi ulipo!Amwe Omwaswepa  
\v 6 Balaita milopa ya bantu ba Lesa, nebashinshimi, nenjamwe mulabapa milopa yakunwa. Celela kubenshileco!”  
\v 7 Popelapo ndalanyumfwa liswi pa nteme akwambeti, “Mwami Lesa wangofu shonse, lombolosho lwenu ni lwa ncinencine kayi lwalulama!” 
\p  
\v 8 Lino mungelo wabusuba waletila ndilo yakendi pa lisuba, nalyo lisuba lyalapewa ngofu sha kutenta bantu ne lubela lwalungula.  
\v 9 Mpobalapya ne lubela lwalungula, balasampula lina lya Lesa ukute ngofu pa malwashi awa. Nomba baliya kuleka bwipishi kwambeti balumbe bukulene bwakendi. 
\p  
\v 10 Mungelo wacisanu waletila ndilo yakendi pa cipuna ca bwami bwa cinyama. Bwami bwa cinyama bwalaba mu mushinshe. Bantu balatatika kuliluma milaka cebo ca kunyumfwa kubaba.  
\v 11 Cebo ca bilonda byali kubaba balamusampula Lesa wakwilu, nikukabeco baliya kuleka kwinsa bintu byaipa. 
\p  
\v 12 Mungelo wa cisanu ne umo waletila ndilo yakendi pa mulonga unene wa Filate. Mulonga walayuma nta! Kwambeti ube nshila ya bami ba kucwe.  
\v 13 Lino ndalabona mishimu itatu yaipa, yalikuboneketi bacula kaipula mu mulomo wa cishinshimwe ne mu mulomo wa cinyama kayi ne mu mulomo wa mushinshimi mubepeshi.  
\v 14 Cakubinga ni mishimu itatu yaipa ilenshinga bikankamanisha. Mishimu itatu iyi, eilenga ku bami bonse mucishi capanshi kubabunganya pamo eti balwane nkondo pa busuba bunene bwa Lesa wa Ngofu Shonse. 
\p  
\v 15 “Kamunyumfwani! Ndesangeti kabwalala! Ukute colwe muntu ulebe, wafwalila limo kayi walibambila. Kutineti katakenda matakosha kayi katakanyumfwa nsoni pa bantu.” 
\p  
\v 16 Lino mishimu yalababunganya bami pa musena umo, uwo ukute kukwiwa mu Cihebeli eti Alamagedon. 
\p  
\v 17 Neye mungelo wa cisanu ne babili waletila ndilo yakendi mwilu mu muya. Liswi lyakompolola lyalanyumfwika ku Cipuna ca Bwami camu Ng'anda ya Lesa kwambeti, “Ee cilenshiki!”  
\v 18 Palaba kubyasha ne kukunkuma ne kutatala kwa mfula kayi ne mutuntumo wa inshi utana ubako mbulengelo mushobo wa bantu.Uwu mutuntumo walikuba waipishisha.  
\v 19 Mutuntumo walapasula munshi unene wa Babulo bibela bitatu, ne minshi naimbi mu cishi conse yalonongeka. Lesa walanuka kayi ewalenshisheti Babulo anwine waini mu nkomeshi yesula bukalu bwakendi.  
\v 20 Nsumbu ne milundu yonse yalashimangana.  
\v 21 Imfula ya mabwe alema makilogalamu ali 50 alikulakila pa bantu balikusampula Lesa cebo ca kupenga ne mfula ya mabwe. 
\c 17  
\s1 Cinyama ne mutukashi mufule 
\p  
\v 1 Lino mungelo umo pa bangelo basanu ne babili basa balikukute ndilo shisanu ne shibili walang'ambileti, “Kwesa ndikuleshe cisubulo Lesa nceti amupe usa mutukashi mufule usa munshi unene webakwa pa menshi angi.  
\v 2 Usa mufule wonanga ne bami ba pacishi capanshi, kayi wakolweshanga bantu waini wa bufule bwakendi.” 
\p  
\v 3 Mpondalekatwa ne Mushimu wa Lesa, mungelo walantwala ku cinyika. Uko nkondalabona mutukashi kaliwatanta pa cinyama cifubela, calikuba calembwa maina mubili wonse akutukana Lesa. Kayi calikukute mitwi isanu ne ibili ne meca likumi.  
\v 4 Mutukashi uyu walikuba wafwala byakufwala bya fubeluka ne byafubela byadula, walikobaika malungu a golide amushobo uliwonse. Walikukute nkomeshi ya golide mu cikasa cakululyo yesula ne bintu byasesemya, kayi byasafwana, bya cabufule bwakendi.  
\v 5 Pa nkumo pakendi palikuba palembwa lina lyashupa kulipandulula, lyakwambeti, “Babulo waya lulumbi, nyabo wa bafule bonse ne bintu bishikusesemya byonse bya mu cishi capanshi.”  
\v 6 Kayi ndalabona mutukashi uyo katantalika, cebo ca milopa njalanwa ya bantu baswepa, kayi ne ya bakamboni ba Yesu mbobalashina. 
\p Mpondalamubona ndalakankamana. 
\p  
\v 7 Lino mungelo walanjipusheti, “Inga nicani ncolakankamananga?” Ninkwambile sha mutukashi uyu, ne sha cinyama ncatantapo ne sha mitwi isanu ne ibili kayi ne sha meca likumi asa.  
\v 8 Cinyama ncolabono calikubako, kayi cilashimangana, cilipepi kupula mucisengu, nomba nicikenga kuya kufwa. Lino bantu bekala pa cishi capanshi, babula kulembwa maina abo mu libuku lya bayumi kacitana cilengwa cishi, bakaboneti cinyama calikubako, calashimangana, kayeti cilesa, nibakakankamane. 
\p  
\v 9 “Pano epalayandikinga mano ne kunyumfwishisha. Mitwi isanu ne ibili isa pekala mutukashi,ilemanininga milundu isanu ne ibili, kayi iyi mitwi isanu ne ibili ilemanininga bami basanu ne babili.  
\v 10 Bami basanu bafwa kendi, umo ucendelesha, wakupwililisha nkana esa. Nomba akesa nakekalowa kacindi kang'ana.”  
\v 11 “Cinyama cisa calikubako, kayi calashimangana cilemanininga mwami wa cisanu ne citatu, uyo eti akapule mu mitwi isanu ne ibili, lino neye nakonongeke.” 
\p  
\v 12 “Nawo meca likumi ngowalabona alemanininga bami likumi batana batatika kwendelesha. Nabo nibakapewe bwami, nibakendeleshe pamo ne cinyama kwa kacindi kang'anowa.  
\v 13 Bami aba bali likumi nibakabe ne muyeyo umo, nibakape ngofu ne bwendeleshi ku cinyama.  
\v 14 Nibakalwane ne Mwana mbelele, lino Mwana mbelele pamo ne bantu bakwiwa bakendi, basalwa, kayi bakute lushomo, nibakabakome, pakwinga Yesu eMwami wa bami bonse.” 
\p  
\v 15 Kayi mungelo walang'ambileti, “Asa menshi ngowabona pekala mutukashi mufule, alemanininga bishi ne bantu bankanda shapusana kayi ne milaka.”  
\v 16 Nawo asa meca likumi ne cinyama ncowalabona nibikamupele mutukashi mufule, ne kumulamuna bintu byonse, ne kumufulula matakosha, nibakalye minyemfu yakendi ne kumutenta pa mulilo.  
\v 17 Pakwinga Lesa nakabike kuyanda kwakendi mu myoyo yabo kwambeti basebensele pamo ne cinyama pakucipa ngofu shakwendelesha mpaka maswi a Lesa akakwanilishiwe. 
\p  
\v 18 “Mutukashi ngowabonanga ni mushi wayampuwo ulendeleshenga bami bonse pa cishi capanshi.” 
\c 18  
\s1 Kuwa kwa mushi Babulo 
\p  
\v 1 Panyuma pakubona mutukashi watanta pa cinyama cifubela, kayi ndalabona naumbi mungelo kaseluka kwilu, ukute ngofu shinene shabwendeleshi, kayi kubala kwakendi kwalamunikila cishi conse ca panshi.  
\v 2 Walompololeti, 
\q1 “Ee, lawu! Babulo waya lulumbi, lawu! 
\q1 Mulaba mwakwikala bibanda 
\q1 ne mishimu yasafwana, 
\q1 kayi ne bikeni byaipa bya mishobo iliyonse. 
\q1  
\v 3 Pakwinga mishobo yonse ilanu bwalwa bwa nyotwa ya bufule bwakendi. 
\q1 Bami pa cishi capanshi balikwinsa bupombo nendiye, 
\q1 nabo beshi makwebo balawininapo pa bufule bwakendi.” 
\p  
\v 4 Kayi ndalanyumfwa maswi kwilu akwambeti, 
\q1 “Kamufumamo bantu bakame! Musonokeni! 
\q1 Kamutamantamo lubasu mu bwipishi bwakendi. Nenjamwe kamutakapewako 
\q1 Cisubulo! 
\q1  
\v 5 Pakwinga bwipishi bwakendi bulashiki kwilu, 
\q1 Neye Lesa lanuku nshila shaipa shamutukashi usa. 
\q1  
\v 6 Kamumwinshilani celana neco ncalamwinshila. 
\q1 Mubwesheleni mankanda abili pa bintu mbyalensa. 
\q1 Isushani nkomesshi yakendi mankanda abili 
\q1 akulula kwa byakunwa mbuli neye ncalamubambila. 
\q1  
\v 7 Mupensheni aungumane 
\q1 kwelana ne lulumbi lwa bwikalo bwa buboni mbwalalipa mwine. 
\q1 Pakwinga ukute kulilumbanya mwine 
\q1 ‘Eti ndekala pano,’ Ndemwami! 
\q1 Ntame mukalubingi, nkana mbapo ne malila!” 
\q1  
\v 8 “Pacebo ici, malwashi, 
\q1 kukolwa ne kulila kayi ne nsala 
\q1 nibikamushikile pa busuba bumo. 
\q1 Kayi nakapye ne mulilo, 
\q1 lino Mwami Lesa nakamomboloshe, 
\q1 pakwinga Lesa niwangofu.” 
\p  
\v 9 Bami ba pacishi capanshi mbwalikwinsa nabo bufule mulunkumbwa lwakendi nibakamulile, bakabona bwishi ne mulilo ulamutentenga.  
\v 10 Nibakemane patali kabebelela nkwalapenshewanga kutineti naboyo ngabapenshewako nibakambengeti, “Akonempa mapensho alenshiki ku munshi unene! Cansoni kuli Babulo! Cindi ca komboloshewa cilashiki.” 
\p  
\v 11 Bashimakwebo pa cishi capanshi nibakalile, pakwinga nipakabule muntu shikula makwebo,  
\v 12 a golide nambi silifa nambi a mabwe a mulo wadula nambi malungu. Paliya eti akaule byakufwala byabo byaina byafubeluka nambi byashilika nambi byafubela nambi citondo ciliconse canunkila nambi ciliconse capangiwa ne munyanga nambi ciliconse capangiwa kucitondo cadula nambi ca mukuba nambi ca cela nambi ca libwe lya mabo.  
\v 13 Kayi paliya eti akauleko Sinamoni nambi twanunkila nambi mafuta anunkila cena nambi lubani nambi bwalwa nambi mafuta a citondo ca ma olifi nambi bunga bwanana nambi maila nambi ng'ombe nambi mbelele nambi mahaki nambi bikoki nambi basha kayi ne bantu.  
\v 14 Bashimakwebo nibakambeti, “Bintu byaina mbyowayandanga bilakupwili, bintu byakobe byaina bilonongeke nteti bakabicanepo.”  
\v 15 Bashimakwebo mbwalawinisha nibakabe ne buyowa nibakemane patali pakubona nceti akapengenga. Nibakamulile malila a nsoni,  
\v 16 kabambeti, “Mama cansoni! Mama cansoni! Obe munshi unene wafwala byakufwala byadula byafubeluka, ne byafubela. Munshi webakwa cena ne golidi ne mabwe adula abeketi malungu.  
\v 17 Ca nsoni pakwinga mu kacindi kang'anowa buboni bwingi bulonongeke!” 
\p Bashikukwasula mato ne muntu uliyense lafumininga kulikonse, basebenshi balikwinsa makwebo Lwenje nibakemane patali,  
\v 18 pakubona bwishi bwa kupya kwakendi. Nibakompololeti, 
\q1 “Ni munshi cini welana ne munshi unene uwu!” 
\p  
\v 19 Balalitukwila bulongo pa mitwi kabompolola, kulila ne kunyumfwa nsoni. Kabambeti, 
\q1 “Mama ca nsoni! Mama ca nsoni! 
\q1 Uwu munshi unene walawinisha bonse balikukute mato cebo ca buboni bwakendi 
\q1 lino muka cindi kang'anowa bonse bulonongeke.” 
\p  
\v 20 Lino kamukondwani Omuli kwilu cebo ca bintu bilamwinshikili. 
\q1 Amwe mwaswepa, amwe batumwa kayi nenjamwe bashinshimi kamukondwani, 
\q1 pakwinga Lesa lamombolosho ne kumupa cisubulo pali ibyo mbyalamwinshilani. 
\p  
\v 21 Mungelo wa ngofu walamanta libwe linene ne kuliwala mu lwenje cubwaa! Ne kwambeti, “Copele cisa nceti ukawalwe panshi mwangofu Babulo munshi unene nteti ukabonekepo sobwe!”  
\v 22 Popelapo balikwimbila ne tulumbu ne tunkobele ne beshikulilisha matolompita kayi ne beshikwimbila nabambi nteti bakanyumfwikepo. Nteti mukacanike kanyuka mpaya nambi maswi a bantu balapelenga bunga.  
\v 23 Malampi akobe nakashimike, ngululu sha cikwati nteti shikanyumfwikepo, pakwinga bashimakwebo bakobe balikuba bacindama pa cishi ca panshi. Kayi mishobo yonse pa cishi ca panshi yalayungaulwa ne buloshi bwakobe. 
\p  
\v 24 Babulo walapewa cisubulo, pakwinga mu munshi mwalacanika milopa ya bashinshimi ne milopa yabantu ba Lesa, ne ya bantu nabambi balashinwa pa cishi ca panshi. 
\c 19  
\s1 Lesa lapanga cisubulo mutukashi mufule 
\p  
\v 1 Panyuma pakendi ndalanyumfwa kuyobeka kwalikunyumfwiketi kwa likoto linene lyabantu kwilu. Kabambeti, “Lupulusho ne bulemeneno kayi ne ngofu ni byakendi Lesa, neco kamumushikaishani!  
\v 2 Lombolosho lwakendi nilwancinencine kayi lwalulama. Lamupa cisubulo mufule wasafwanyanga bantu pa cishi ca panshi ne bufule bwakendi. Walashina bantu ba Lesa, neco Lesa lamubweshele.”  
\v 3 Kayi likoto linene lisa lyalompololeti, “Lesa ashikaishiwe! Bwishi bwa mulilo ulatente munshi unene ulasukumunga kwa muyayaya!”  
\v 4 Bamakulene makumi abili ne bana kayi ne bya buyumi bina balasuntama panshi ne kukambilila Lesa walikuba wekala pa Cipuna ca Bwami kabambeti, “Ameni! Lesa ashikaishiwe!” 
\s1 Bwinga bwa Mwana Mbelele 
\p  
\v 5 Lino ku Cipuna ca Bwami kwalanyufwika liswi lyalikwambeti, “Kamushikaishani Lesa, mobasebenshi bakendi pamo ne bantu bonse omukute kumutina, bamakulene ne batwanike.”  
\v 6 Kayi ndalanyumfwa maswi alikunyumfwiketi kuyobeka kwa bantu bangi. Alikunyumfwiketi kuwota kwa menshi angi nambi eti kutatala kwa mfula, kabambeti, “Katushikaishani Lesa! Pakwinga Mwami Lesa wetu wa ngofu shonse latatiki kwendelesha.”  
\v 7 Katukondwani, kayi tusamwe, tumupe bulemu, pakwinga cindi ca bwinga bwa Mwana Mbelele cilashiki kayi mutukashi ngwalayandanga kweba neye walibambila.  
\v 8 Lesa lamupa byakufwala bya swepa, byabeka, kwambeti afwale. Byakufwala bilemanininga micito yaina njobakute bantu ba Lesa. 
\p  
\v 9 Lino mungelo walang'ambileti, “Kolembeti, ‘Bakute colwe bantu balakwiwa ku bwinga bwa Mwana Mbelele.’ ” Kayi mungelo walambeti, “Awa ni maswi a ancine ncine Lesa.” 
\p  
\v 10 Popelapo ndalasuntama pantangu pakendi kuyanda kumukambilila, mwakufwambana walambeti, “Sobwe kotenseco! Ame ndemusha mbuli ncobele pamo ne banobe bashoma. Kambilila Lesa!” 
\p Pakwinga cancine ncine ncalayubulula Yesu ecilapanga ngofu bantu kwamba mulumbe wa Lesa. 
\s1 Watanta Lihaki lituba 
\p  
\v 11 Kwilu mpokwalacaluka, ndalabona lihaki lituba. Walikuba watantapo walikukwiweti, “Washomeka” Kayi “Wa ncinencine.” Nendi ukute kombolosha, nekulwana nkondo.  
\v 12 Menso akendi alyeti lubela lwa mulilo, ku mutwi walikuba wafwala ngowani shingi sha bwami, ne lina ndyalikuba walembwa nkalyeshibikwa nsombi mwinowa eulinshi.  
\v 13 Walikuba wafwala mwinjila wananankana milopa. Lina lyakendi ni “Maswi a Lesa.”  
\v 14 Makoto a nkondo a kwilu alamukonkela, kali atanta pamahaki atuba, nawo kali afwala minjila ituba yaswepa mbee!  
\v 15 Mu mulomo mwakendi mwalapula cibeshi calumata ico ncalakomenako mishobo ya bantu. Yesu Klistu nakabendeleshe ne nkoli ya cela, kayi nakalyataule mucisengu mwakutyanina minyansa ya bukalu bwa Lesa wa Ngofu Shonse.  
\v 16 Pa mwinjila ne pa libelo lyakendi palikuba palembwa lina, lyakwambeti “Mwami wa Bami ne Mwendeleshi wa bendeleshi.” 
\p  
\v 17 Kayi ndalabona mungelo kali wemana pa lisuba. Walompolola kukuwa bikeni byonse bilaulukunga mwilu kambeti, “Kamwisani mubungane pamo ku malyalya anene ngwalamubambili Lesa.  
\v 18 Mwise mulye mitunta ya bami ne ya bamakulene ba nkondo ne ya bashilikali ne ya batanta pa mahaki, minyemfu ya bantu bonse basha ne babula kuba basha, bamakulene kayi ne batwanike!” 
\p  
\v 19 Lino ndalabona cinyama ne bami ba pacishi capanshi ne makoto abo ankondo balabungana pamo kwambeti balwane ne walikuba watanta pa lihaki ne likoto lyakendi.  
\v 20 Balacikata cinyama pamo ne mushinshimi mubepeshi walikwinsa byeshikukankamanisha. Mbyecalikwinsa ebyalikubepa bantu balikukambilila cikoshano ca cinyama kabakute cishibisho caco. Bonse babili cinyama ne mushinshimi mubepeshi, balawalwa mu lwenje lwa mulilo ulabangilinga ne sulufule.  
\v 21 Cibeshi calafuma mu mulomo wa uyo walikuba watanta lihaki encalashinishako makoto abo a nkondo, bikeni byonse byalekuta kulya minyemfu yabo. 
\c 20  
\s1 Byaka cina cimo (1000) 
\p  
\v 1 Kayi ndalabona mungelo kaseluka kwilu kakute cakucalwisha kucisengu citali kayi ne ncetani yalema mu makasa.  
\v 2 Walacitanya cishinshimwe cikulukulu cisa cikute kukwiweti Satana nambi Muyungaushi, ne kumusunga ncetani kwabyaka cina cimo.  
\v 3 Mungelo usa walamuwala Satana mu cisengu citali walacalapo kayi ne kubikapo cidindo cilambangeti nteti akayungaulepo mishobo ya bantu mpaka pakapite byaka cina cimo. Panyuma pakendi nakasungululwe kwa kacindi kang'ana. 
\p  
\v 4 Ndalabona bipuna bya Bwami palikuba pekala abo balapewa ngofu sha kombolosha, kayi ndalabona mishimu ya abo balatimbulwa mitwi cebo ca kukambauka cancinencine ncalayubululwa Yesu kayi nepacebo camaswi a Lesa. Aba ebantu balabula kukambilila cinyama nambi mukoshano waco, kayi baliya kutambula ne kulembwa cishibisho pa nkumo nambi pa bikasa byabo.Balapunduka ne kwendelesha pamo ne Klistu kwa byaka cina cimo  
\v 5 Bantu bangi bafwa baliya kupunduka mpaka ku mapwililisho a byaka cina cimo. Uku ekupunduka kwa kutanguna kwa bantu bafwa.  
\v 6 Bakute colwe cinene ni bantu beti bakacane lubasu mu kupundushiwa kwa kutanguna kwa bantu bafwa. Lufu lwa cibili luliya ngofu palyendibo, nibakabe beshimilumbo ba Lesa ne Klistu kayi nibakendeleshe pamo nendiye kwa byaka cina cimo. 
\s1 Satana lakomwa 
\p  
\v 7 Byakapwa byaka cina cimo Satana nakasungululwe mujele,  
\v 8 kayi nakenga akuyungaula mishobo mu mbasu shina shapa cishi capanshi, mishobo ikute kukwiweti Gogi ne Magogi. Satana nakababunganye pamo bantu bangi eti museya wa mu mulonga kwambeti balibambile kulwana nkondo.  
\v 9 Balamwaikila pa cishi conse capanshi balaushinguluka musasa bantu ba Lesa ne munshi ngwasuni. Nsombi kwalesa mulilo kwilu walabononga bonse.  
\v 10 Lino Satana walikubayungaula balamuwala mu lwenje lwa mulilo wa sulufule, uko cinyama cisa ne mushinshimi mubepeshi nkobalikuba bawalwa. Uko nkoti bakapenshewenga munshi ne mashiku kwamuyaya. 
\s1 Lombolosho lwa kupwililisha 
\p  
\v 11 Lino ndalabona cipuna ca Bwami cituba cinene, cishi ne kwilu byalamubundumuka uyo walikuba wekalapo, kayi biliya kubonekapo.  
\v 12 Kayi ndalabona bantu bafwa bamakulene ne batwanike kabali bemana ku cipuna ca Bwami. Mabuku alacalulwa, kayi libuku nalimbi lyalacalulwa, ili elibuku lya buyumi. Bafwa nibakomboloshewe kwelana ne micito yabo yalembwa mu mabuku awo.  
\v 13 Neco lwenje lwalapulisha balafwilamo, nalo lufu ne cishi cabafu byalapulisha abo balikubamo. Bonse balomboloshewa kwelana ne micito njobalikwinsa.  
\v 14 Lino lufu ne cishi cabafu byalawalwa mu lwenje lwa mulilo. lwenje lwa mulilo elufu lwa cibili.  
\v 15 Bonse balabula kulembwa maina mu libuku lya buyumi balawalwa mu lwenje lwa mulilo. 
\c 21  
\s1 Kwilu kwa linolino ne cishi capanshi calinolino 
\p  
\v 1 Panyuma pakendi, ndalabona mwilu kwa linolino ne cishi ca panshi ca linolino. Mwilu mwa kutanguna ne cishi ca panshi cakutanguna kayi ne lwenje byalashimangana.  
\v 2 Kayi ndalabona Munshi Uswepa Yelusalemu wa linolino kauseluka kwilu kuli Lesa, wabambwa cena mbuli nabwinga ncakute kufwala cena ayanga kukumana ne ibendi.  
\v 3 Ndalanyumfwa liswi ku Cipuna ca Bwami lyalikompololeti, “Kamubonani lino ng'anda ya Lesa ili pakati pa bantu, nakekale nabo pamo. Nabo nibakekale nendi! Nibakabe bantu bakendi, nendi nakabe Lesa wabo.  
\v 4 Nakabapukute misoshi yonsepa menso. Nteti pakabe lufu nambi kulila mibila nambi kunyumfwa bishikubaba. Bintu byalikubako pakutanguna bilapiti.” 
\p  
\v 5 Lino wekala pa cipuna ca Bwami walambeti, “Ndabambanga bintu byonse kuba byalinolino!” Kayi walambeti, “Kolemba pakwinga maswi ngondambanga na ncinencine kayi ashomeka.”  
\v 6 Kayi walang'ambileti, “Bilenshiki! Njame Alefa ne Omega, wakutanguna kayi ne wakupwililisha. Ninkasuminishe uliyense ukute nyotwa kunwa pansansa, menshi eshikupa buyumi alapupunga nteti bakaulenga sobwe.  
\v 7 Ninkape ibi bintu ku bantu beshibakakome, kayi ninkabe Lesa wabo, naboyo nibakabe bantu bakame.  
\v 8 Nomba bayowa ne babula lushomo ne basafwana beshikwinsa byaipa, bakapondo ne bafule ne bang'anga ne beshi kukambilila tumbwanga kayi ne bonse bandemi shibili, cakutambula cabo nicikabe lwenje lulabangilinga mulilo wa sulufule, ulu elufu lwa cibili.” 
\s1 Yelusalemu walinolino 
\p  
\v 9 Kwalesa umo wa bangelo basanu ne babili basa balikukute Indilo shisanu ne shibili shesula malwashi asanu ne abili walang'ambileti, “Kwesa kuno ndikuleshe moye, mukashi wa Mwana Mbelele.”  
\v 10 Neco Mushimu Uswepa walamfukata, neye mungelo walantwala pa mulundu unene kayi utali, kuyakundesha Munshi Uswepa, Yelusalemu walikuseluka kwilu kuli Lesa,  
\v 11 walikubeka ne bulemeneno bwa Lesa. Uwo munshi walikubeketi libwe lya mulo waduleti libwe lyeshima likute kukwiweti yasipi lyatuba tuu eti gilasi.  
\v 12 Uwo munshi walikukute luba lunene kayi lutali, kayi walikukute bishinga likumi ne bibili, pacishinga cimo ne cimo palikuba mungelo walikupembelela. Pabishinga palikuba palembwa maina likumi ne abili a bana Baislayeli.  
\v 13 Ca kucwe kwa munshi kwalikuba bishinga bitatu, ca kunyika bishinga bitatu, cakumusansa bishinga bitatu, kayi ca kumbonshi bishinga bitatu.  
\v 14 Luba lwa munshi lwalebakwa palulindu lwa mabwe anene, pa libwe limo ne limo palikuba palembwa lina lya umo wa batumwa likumi ne babili ba Mwana Mbelele.  
\v 15 Lino mungelo walikwamba ne njame walikukute litete lya golide lyakupimisha munshi ne bishinga kayi ne luba.  
\v 16 munshi uwo walikuba ne mbasu shina shelana, mubutali ne mubufupi mwalikuba mwelana. mungelo walaupimisha uwo munshi ne litete nekucana makilomita bina bibili ne myanda makumi ana Mubutali ne mubufupi kayi ne mushimba byonse byalikuba byelana.  
\v 17 Kayi walapima luba, walacaneti ni lutali ntamwa makumi asanu ne limo Kwelana ne mpimino ya muntu yelana kayi ne mpimino ya mungelo.  
\v 18 Luba lwalikuba lwebakwa ne mabwe a Yasipi. Munshi uwo balawibakisha negolide winewine wabeketi gilasi.  
\v 19 Lulindu lwa luba lwa munshi lwalikuba lwamabwe apusana pusana adula. Libwe lyakutanguna lya lulindu lyalikuba lya yasipi libwe lya cibili lya safilo lya citatu lya kalikedo, lya cina lya emalodi.  
\v 20 libwe lya cisanu lya sadonu, libwe ca cisanu ne cimo lya sadiyo, libwe ca cisanu ne bibili lya kulusolito, libwe ca cisanu ne citatu lyalikuba belulo, libwe ca cisanu ne cina lya topazi, libwe ca likumi lya kakedoni, libwe ca likumi ne cimo lya huwakinto, libwe ca likumi ne bibili lyalikuba ametusito.  
\v 21 Bishinga bya munshi likumi ne bibili byalikukute mukanda wa malungu adula ali likumi nabili, pacishinga ciliconse palikuba mukanda wa bulungu bumo bunene. Mukwakwa unene mu munshi walikuba wa golidi winewine waswepeti gilasi. 
\p  
\v 22 Lino umo mu munshi ndiya kubonamo Ng'anda ya kupaililamo Lesa, pakwinga Mwami Lesa Wangofu Shonse kayi ne Mwana Mbelele. ebalikuba ng'anda ya kupaillilamo  
\v 23 Kumunika kwa lisuba ne mwenshi nkakwali kuyandika umo mu munshi sobwe, pakwinga bulemeneno bwa Lesa ebulamunikilinga, neye Mwana Mbelele elampi lya munshi.  
\v 24 Mishobo yonse pa cishi ca panshi nikendenga mumuni eti ukafumenga mu munshi. Kayi ne bendeleshi ba pacishi capanshi nibakaletemo buboni bwabo.  
\v 25 Pakwinga bishinga byamunshi nteti bakabicalenga munshi wonse kayi nteti kukabenga mashiku.  
\v 26 Mumunshi umo mishobo yonse yamucishi capanshi nibakaletemo bulemeneno ne buboni bwabo.  
\v 27 Kuliya cintu casafwana eti cikengilemo nambi muntu lenshinga bishikuleta nsoni nambi mubepeshi eti akengilemo. Abo balembwa maina mu libuku lya buyumi lya Mwana mbelele ebonka beshi bakengilemo. 
\c 22  
\p  
\v 1 Lino mungelo walandesha mulonga wa menshi eshikupa buyumi. Aswepeti gilasi kapupa kufumina panshi pa cipuna ca Bwami ca Lesa ne ca Mwana Mbelele.  
\v 2 Mulonga uwo walikuba wantabankana pa mukwakwa wa mu munshi. Kutala konse konse kwa mulonga kwalikuba citondo cikute bisepo byeshikupa buyumi. Byalikusema bisepo kankanda kamo pa mwenshi kwa myenshi likumi ne ibili. Mishobo pacishi capanshi nibakasebenseshe matewu kushilikisha malwashi abo.  
\v 3 Paliya cintu cashinganwa ne Lesa etici kacanike mumunshi uwo. 
\p Pakwinga Cipuna ca Lesa ne ca Mwana mbelele nicikabenga mukati mu munshi, Umo basebenshi bakendi mweshi bakamukambililenga.  
\v 4 Kayi nibakamubone menso ne menso, kayi lina lyakendi nilikalembwe pa nkumo pabo.  
\v 5 Mashiku nteti akabeko sobwe nambi mumuni wa lampi nambi wa lisuba, pakwinga Mwami Lesa nakabe mumuni wabo. Nibakendelesheti bami kwamuyayaya. 
\s1 Kwisa kayi kwa Yesu 
\p  
\v 6 Lino mungelo walang'ambileti, “Maswi onse ngolanyumfu na ncinencine kayi ashomeka. Kayi Mwami Lesa ukute kupa bashinshimi bakendi Mushimu wakendi Uswepa, ewalatuma mungelo kuya kwishibisha basebenshi ba Lesa kwambeti beshibe bintu byeshi binshike calinolino apa.” 
\p  
\v 7 Yesu lambangeti, “Nyumfwani! Ndesanga lino lino! Bakute colwe bantu balanyumfunga maswi abushinshimi ali mu libuku ili.” 
\p  
\v 8 Njame Yohane ndalanyumfwa ne kubibona ibi bintu. Mpondalabinyumfwa ne kubibona ndalawa panshi pa myendo ya mungelo walikundesha ibi bintu. Neco ndalayandeti ndi mukambilile.  
\v 9 Nsombi neye mungelo walang'ambileti, “Sobwe kotenseco, ame ndemusebenshi munobe pamo ne banse bobe bashinshimi kayi ne bonse balakonkelenga maswi ali mu libuku ili. Kambilila Lesa!”  
\v 10 Kayi walang'ambileti, “Maswi abushinshimi ali mu libuku ili nakwesha kwasoleka, pakwinga cindi cakwinshika bintu ibi cilipepi.  
\v 11 Muntu uyo wakakatilowa kwinsa byaipa apitilishe, neye wasafwana apitilishe kuba wasafwana. Nomba neye walulama apitilishe kwinsa byaina, neye waswepa apitilishe kuba waswepa.” 
\p  
\v 12 Yesu lambangeti, “Kamubonani! Ndesanga lino lino! nkute cilambo cakupa uliyense kwelana ne ncito nshalikwinsa.  
\v 13 Ame njame mutanshi kayi wakunyuma, wakutanguna kayi njame wakupwililisha.” 
\p  
\v 14 Bakute colwe bacapa minganjo yabo kwambeti babe ne colwe cakulyako bisepo bya citondo ca buyumi ne kuya kwingila pa cishinga ca munshi.  
\v 15 Nomba bantu bakute bwikalo bulyeti bwa ba kabwa ne beshikwinsa sha buloshi ne sha bupombo ne bukapondo ne beshikukambilila tumbwanga kayi ne bandemi shibili nteti bakengile mumunshi uwo pimbi.  
\v 16 “Ame Yesu njame ndalatuma mungelo kwisa kumwambila amwe bintu ibi amwe muli mu mibungano. Njame wa mu mukowa wa Dafeti, njame ntanda, nyenyenshi ya kumaca.” 
\p  
\v 17 Mushimu Uswepa ne nabwinga wa Mwana Mbelele balambangeti, “Kamwisani!” 
\p Muntu lanyumfunga neye ambeti, “Kamwisani!” 
\p Muntu lanyumfunga nyotwa ese atambule menshi abuyumi abula mulo. 
\s1 Maswi akupwililisha 
\p  
\v 18 Ame Yohane ndacenjeshenga muntu uliyense lanyumfunga maswi abushinshimi ali mu libuku ili. Na muntu ubikilapo pamaswi awa, Neye Lesa nakamubikileko cisubulo ca malwashi ambwa mu libuku ili.  
\v 19 Kayi na muntu uliyense wela kufunyako maswi abushinshimi bwa mu libuku ili, neye Lesa nakafunyeko colwe cakulya bisepo bya citondo ca buyumi, kayi nteti akengile mu munshi waswepa mbuli ncecalembwa mu libuku ili. 
\p  
\v 20 Uyo lenshilinga bukamboni ku bintu ibi lambangeti, “Cakubinga! Ndesanga lino lino!” 
\p Kacibeco! Kamwisani Mwami Yesu! 
\p  
\v 21 Kwina moyo kwa Mwami Yesu shibe nenu mwense. Ameni.